('1132', 'urine', '尿', '<img src=\"E5B0BF.png\" />', 'urine, flag, water', '7', '29', 'Animals use their urine to mark their territory. So for them, their body water works as a flag denoting their \"country\" (why bother? we all know which story you are going to pick).', 'JH', '1', 'ニョウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('1133', 'nun', '尼', '<img src=\"E5B0BC.png\" />', 'nun, flag, spoon, sitting on the ground', '5', '29', 'Red cross nuns sit in a tent under the red cross flag, spooning out food to the hungry.', 'JH', '1', 'ニ', 'あま', NULL, NULL),
('1134', 'buttocks', '尻', '<img src=\"E5B0BB.png\" />', 'buttocks, flag, nine, baseball', '5', '29', 'The baseball team stick flags in their buttocks and wave them at the opposing team to put them off.', 'JH', '', 'コウ', 'しり', NULL, NULL),
('1135', 'mud', '泥', '<img src=\"E6B3A5.png\" />', 'mud, water, water droplets, water pistol, nun, flag, spoon, sitting on the ground', '8', '29', 'TV gets weirder and weirder... Now they´re doing mud wrestling shows with nuns splashing around in the water. What will they think of next?', 'JH', '2', 'デイ、ナイ、デ、ニ', 'どろ', NULL, NULL),
('1136', 'fence', '塀', '<img src=\"E5A180.png\" />', 'fence, soil, dirt, ground, folding screen, flag, puzzle, horns, two hands', '12', '29', '[fence; wall; (kokuji)] A fence separates one soil from the other. On a large scale, large pieces of soils in the world have a virtual fence called nation. Picture a world map where all countries have their soil with one color, their national flag as the legend and a fence on the borders... don´t you think it looks like a giant puzzle?', 'JH', '1', 'ヘイ、ベイ', '', NULL, NULL),
('1137', 'footgear', '履', '<img src=\"E5B1A5.png\" />', 'footgear, flag, restore, Nelson, column, going, line, fold back, double back, reclining, lying down, sun, day, walking legs', '15', '29', 'NOTE: The most common use is in はく, meaning to put on footgear, rather than actual footgear itself. STORY: You are asleep in camp when you are woken up with news that the FLAG has fallen to the enemy. You quickly PUT ON YOUR FOOTGEAR and run off to RESTORE the FLAG.', 'JH', '1', 'リ', 'は.く', NULL, NULL),
('1138', 'roof', '屋', '<img src=\"E5B18B.png\" />', 'roof, flag, climax, wall, one, ceiling, elbow, soil, dirt, ground', '9', '29', 'Flag at the climax (highest point) of a castle roof.', '3', '4', 'オク', 'や', NULL, NULL),
('1139', 'grip', '握', '<img src=\"E68FA1.png\" />', 'grip, finger, fingers, roof, flag climax, wall, one, ceiling, elbow, soil, dirt, ground', '12', '29', 'Fingers gripping the roof as your about to fall to your death. Think of an action scene in some movie.', 'JH', '1', 'アク', 'にぎ.る', NULL, NULL),
('114', 'evening', '夕', '<img src=\"E5A495.png\" />', 'evening', '3', '7', 'The evening is young, the moon is not full.', '1', '4', 'セキ', 'ゆう', NULL, NULL),
('1140', 'yield', '屈', '<img src=\"E5B188.png\" />', 'yield, flag, exit', '8', '29', 'When yielding, soldiers raise the white flag before exiting from the trenches.', 'JH', '1', 'クツ', 'かが.む、かが.める', NULL, NULL),
('1141', 'dig', '掘', '<img src=\"E68E98.png\" />', 'dig, finger, fingers, yield, flag, exit', '11', '29', 'If you dig with your fingers hard enough, soil eventually yields.', 'JH', '2', 'クツ', 'ほ.る', NULL, NULL),
('1142', 'ditch', '堀', '<img src=\"E5A080.png\" />', 'ditch, moat, soil, dirt, ground, yield, flag, exit', '11', '29', '(See dig (#1061)). When soil finally yielded thanks to your digging efforts, what you have is a ditch.', 'JH', '1', 'クツ', 'ほり', NULL, NULL),
('1143', 'reside', '居', '<img src=\"E5B185.png\" />', 'reside, flag, old, tombstone, gravestone, church, ten, needle, mouth', '8', '29', 'A humongous American flag in Florida marks the place where all the old people reside.', '5', '3', 'キョ、コ', 'い.る、-い、お.る', NULL, NULL),
('1144', 'set', '据', '<img src=\"E68DAE.png\" />', 'set, finger, fingers, reside, flag, old, tombstone, gravestone, church, ten, needle, mouth', '11', '29', 'The man set his finger firmly on the map and said \"Here is where they reside, I am certain of it\".', 'JH', '1', 'キョ', 'す.える、す.わる', NULL, NULL),
('1145', 'hem', '裾', '<img src=\"E8A3BE.png\" />', 'hem, cloak, reside, flag, old, tombstone, gravestone, church, ten, needle, mouth', '13', '29', 'Something is residing in the hem of your cloak. Maybe you should consider cleaning it? キョ コ すそ cuff; hem; foot of mountain.', 'JH', '', 'キョ、コ', 'すそ', NULL, NULL),
('1146', 'stratum', '層', '<img src=\"E5B1A4.png\" />', 'stratum, flag, increase, formerly, horns, rice field, brains, sun, day', '14', '29', 'The strata have piled up in an ever increasing pile of dirt. As the geologists go down the rocks, they flag each stratum with the name of the corresponding era.', '6', '2', 'ソウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('1147', 'bureau', '局', '<img src=\"E5B180.png\" />', 'bureau, flag, phrase, bound up, mouth', '7', '29', 'The Federal Bureau of Investigation has email scanners that flag certain phrases.', '3', '3', 'キョク', 'つぼね', NULL, NULL),
('1148', 'slow', '遅', '<img src=\"E98185.png\" />', 'slow, flag, sheep, road', '12', '29', 'A sheep crossing guard waves a SLOW flag for his fellow sheep crossing the road.', 'JH', '3', 'チ', 'おく.れる、おく.らす、おそ.い', NULL, NULL),
('1149', 'leak', '漏', '<img src=\"E6BC8F.png\" />', 'leak, water, water droplets, water pistol, flag, rain, weather', '14', '29', 'WATER always LEAKED in the spot left by the FLAG planted in the roof everytime it RAINED. Not too hard to picture a hole left in the ceiling from a flag, now leaking water.', 'JH', '1', 'ロウ', 'も.る、も.れる、も.らす', NULL, NULL),
('115', 'eventide', '汐', '<img src=\"E6B190.png\" />', 'eventide, water, water droplets, water pistol, evening', '6', '7', 'Eventide is just another word for evening, and it has the word tide in it which we associate with water.', 'Nam', '1', 'セキ', 'しお、うしお、せい', NULL, NULL);
