('1261', 'Big Dipper', '斗', '<img src=\"E69697.png\" />', 'big dipper, measuring cup, big dipper, The Plough, drop, ten, needle', '4', '31', 'Since the meaning of \"big dipper\" is rather specific and the sense of measurement seems to be a more common usage, I concentrate on the primative meaning of measuring cup. This is a pictograph, with the first two strokes representing the measuring ticks on the side of the cup.', 'JH', '1', 'ト、トウ', '', NULL, NULL),
