('1298', 'printing block', '版', '<img src=\"E78988.png\" />', 'printing block, one-sided, waiter with wine on tray, anti-, demonstration, cliff, crotch', '8', '32', 'Before the advent of printers in Japan, typewriters couldn´t be built as they were in the west due to how many kanji there are. Lots of small printing blocks had to be used instead. One side of the printing block would have a mirrored (anti) image of the kanji. This is true.', '5', '2', 'ハン', '', NULL, NULL),
('1299', 'of', '之', '<img src=\"E4B98B.png\" />', 'of, Zorro, building blocks, zig-zag', '3', '32', 'Of all the kanji, this is the only one 之orro can write.', 'Nam', '1', 'シ', 'の、これ、おいて、ゆく、この', NULL, NULL),
('13', 'month', '月', '<img src=\"E69C88.png\" />', 'month, moon, month, flesh, part of the body', '4', '1', 'A month is longer than a day.', '1', '5', 'ゲツ、ガツ', 'つき', NULL, NULL),
('130', 'exquisite', '妙', '<img src=\"E5A699.png\" />', 'exquisite, woman, few', '7', '7', 'Exquisite women are few and far between.', 'JH', '1', 'ミョウ、ビョウ', 'たえ', NULL, NULL),
('1300', 'destitution', '乏', '<img src=\"E4B98F.png\" />', 'destitution, drop, of, Zorro, building blocks, zig-zag', '4', '32', 'Children in complete destitution have no hope of ever getting toys to play with, so when they find even a tiny drop of a building block they are overjoyed.', 'JH', '1', 'ボウ', 'とぼ.しい、とも.しい', NULL, NULL),
('1301', 'turf', '芝', '<img src=\"E88A9D.png\" />', 'turf, flowers, of, Zorro, building blocks, zig-zag', '6', '32', 'Artificial turf made easy: flowers stuck on top of building blocks that you can place anywhere.', 'JH', '1', 'シ', 'しば', NULL, NULL),
('1302', 'negative', '不', '<img src=\"E4B88D.png\" />', 'negative, one, ceiling, person, drop', '4', '32', '[Smithsonian] Scene: Mr. T hanging from the ceiling being tortured. He is asked if he is going to talk. Spitting (a drop of saliva) in the torturer´s face, he says \"Negative\".', '4', '4', 'フ、ブ', '', NULL, NULL),
('1303', 'negate', '否', '<img src=\"E590A6.png\" />', 'negate, negative, mouth', '7', '32', 'To distinguish between 否 negate, and 不 negative (#1217): Note that negate contains 口, which is a kind of gate.', '6', '3', 'ヒ', 'いな、いや', NULL, NULL),
('1304', 'cupfuls', '杯', '<img src=\"E69DAF.png\" />', 'cupfuls, tree, wood, negative', '8', '32', 'The maple tree is very negative about it, but the farmer still collects cupfuls of maple syrup from it.', 'JH', '3', 'ハイ', 'さかずき', NULL, NULL),
('1305', 'dart', '矢', '<img src=\"E79FA2.png\" />', 'dart, drop, heavens', '5', '33', 'Zeus ran out of lightning bolts and has to drop darts from the heavens.', '2', '1', 'シ', 'や', NULL, NULL),
('1306', 'rectify', '矯', '<img src=\"E79FAF.png\" />', 'rectify, dart, drop, heavens, angel, heavens, mouth, hood, mouth, mouth2', '17', '33', 'Angels have now been given a powerful tool to rectify human behavior instantly, without delay - they have been allowed to drop darts on those who misbehave... spare the dart and spoil the man...', 'JH', '1', 'キョウ', 'た.める', NULL, NULL),
('1307', 'tribe', '族', '<img src=\"E6978F.png\" />', 'tribe, banner, direction, compass, direction, reclining, lying down, dart, drop, heavens', '11', '33', 'With a banner declaring \"Keep Out!\" and blow darts to back it up, the Amazon tribe is not that friendly.', '3', '4', 'ゾク', '', NULL, NULL),
('1308', 'know', '知', '<img src=\"E79FA5.png\" />', 'know, dart, drop, heavens, mouth', '8', '33', 'I should know. After all, I did graduate from Dartmouth!', '2', '4', 'チ', 'し.る、し.らせる', NULL, NULL),
('1309', 'wisdom', '智', '<img src=\"E699BA.png\" />', 'wisdom, know, dart, drop, heavens, mouth, sun, day, tongue wagging', '12', '33', 'Wisdom is knowing everything OVER the sun (fools assume everything UNDER).', 'Nam', '1', 'チ', '', NULL, NULL),
('131', 'focus', '省', '<img src=\"E79C81.png\" />', 'focus, few, eye', '9', '7', 'You focus by concentrating your eye on fewer objects.', '4', '2', 'セイ、ショウ', 'かえり.みる、はぶ.く', NULL, NULL),
('1310', 'shove', '挨', '<img src=\"E68CA8.png\" />', 'shove, finger, fingers, elbow, dart, drop, heavens', '10', '33', 'In the busy pub, one of the dart players shoved his dart into my elbow by accident when it nearly slipped out of his fingers.', 'JH', '', 'アイ', 'ひら.く', NULL, NULL),
('1311', 'halberd', '矛', '<img src=\"E79F9B.png\" />', 'halberd, beforehand', '5', '33', 'マオ Zedong always carried a halberd.', 'JH', '1', 'ム、ボウ', 'ほこ', NULL, NULL),
('1312', 'tender', '柔', '<img src=\"E69F94.png\" />', 'tender, halberd, beforehand, tree, wood', '9', '33', '[tender; weakness; gentleness; softness] Love me tender, Love me perfect, Never cheat on me. Or I´ll impale you on my Halberd, And hang ya atop a tree...', 'JH', '2', 'ジュウ、ニュウ', 'やわ.らか、やわ.らかい、やわ、やわ.ら', NULL, NULL),
('1313', 'task', '務', '<img src=\"E58B99.png\" />', 'task, halberd, beforehand, taskmaster, power, muscle, arnold', '11', '33', 'It is with the halberd he holds that the taskmaster exerts his power over those actually performing the task.', '5', '3', 'ム', 'つと.める', NULL, NULL),
('1314', 'fog', '霧', '<img src=\"E99CA7.png\" />', 'fog, rain, weather, task, halberd, beforehand, taskmaster, power, muscle, arnold', '19', '33', 'This fog is the perfect weather for us to perform our task undetected.', 'JH', '1', 'ム、ボウ、ブ', 'きり', NULL, NULL),
('1315', 'squad', '班', '<img src=\"E78FAD.png\" />', 'squad, sword, spear, cutlass, king, jewel, ball, king2, jewel2, ball2', '10', '33', 'Am I the only one who took this as penis and balls? In order to be in the man-squad, naturally you need to have two balls with your \"spear\" in the middle there.', '6', '1', 'ハン', '', NULL, NULL),
('1316', 'homecoming', '帰', '<img src=\"E5B8B0.png\" />', 'homecoming, sword, spear, cutlass, feather duster, broom, apron, crown, towel', '10', '33', 'A female warrior returns home from battle. Her husband takes away her spear to symbolize the end of fighting and gives her a broom and an apron. “Boy, this is some kind of HOMECOMING,” thinks the veteran. (Adapted from johnskb).', '2', '4', 'キ', 'かえ.る、かえ.す、おく.る、とつ.ぐ', NULL, NULL),
('1317', 'bow', '弓', '<img src=\"E5BC93.png\" />', 'bow', '3', '33', 'My personification for this primative is Legolas from the Lord of the Rings: a master at the bow. I suppose robin hood etc would work too.', '2', '1', 'キュウ', 'ゆみ', NULL, NULL),
('1318', 'pull', '引', '<img src=\"E5BC95.png\" />', 'pull, bow, stick', '4', '33', 'Put a walking stick in the bow and pull it back, ready to fire at the geezer.', '2', '3', 'イン', 'ひ.く、ひ.き、ひ.き-、-び.き、ひ.ける', NULL, NULL),
('1319', 'condolences', '弔', '<img src=\"E5BC94.png\" />', 'condolences, bow, walking stick', '4', '33', 'Perhaps a pictograph of a soldier´s weapons--his sword and bow-placed ceremonially over his body before burial, while people offer their condolences.', 'JH', '1', 'チョウ', 'とむら.う、とぶら.う', NULL, NULL),
('132', 'thick', '厚', '<img src=\"E58E9A.png\" />', 'thick, cliff, sun, day, child', '9', '7', 'In Sparta we throw our Children over a Cliff. Under the Sun, they fight other Children. In the end, if they survive, they sure have thick skin.', '5', '2', 'コウ', 'あつ.い、あか', NULL, NULL),
('1320', 'vast', '弘', '<img src=\"E5BC98.png\" />', 'vast, bow, elbow', '5', '33', 'If you pull the bow back with your elbow, you can shoot a vast distance.', 'Nam', '1', 'コウ、グ', 'ひろ.い', NULL, NULL),
('1321', 'strong', '強', '<img src=\"E5BCB7.png\" />', 'strong, bow, elbow, insect', '11', '33', 'An insect who can fly vast distances is strong.', '2', '4', 'キョウ、ゴウ', 'つよ.い、つよ.まる、つよ.める、し.いる、こわ.い', NULL, NULL),
('1322', 'more and more', '弥', '<img src=\"E5BCA5.png\" />', 'more and more, bow, hammock, reclining, lying down, small, little', '8', '33', 'The bow dug more and more into the small of his back as he reclined on it. Will someone please tell the idiot to get up?', 'JH', '1', 'ミ、ビ', 'いや、や、あまねし、いよいよ、とおい、ひさし、ひさ.しい、わた.る', NULL, NULL),
('1323', 'weak', '弱', '<img src=\"E5BCB1.png\" />', 'weak, bow, ice, bow2, ice2', '10', '33', 'Two weak archers agree on a duel to the death. They constantly shoot at each other but never manage to hit their target. But what they lack in skill they make up in determination, and they keep shooting for hours, and days, and months, until it´s wintertime and their bows are coated in ice.', '2', '2', 'ジャク', 'よわ.い、よわ.る、よわ.まる、よわ.める', NULL, NULL),
('1324', 'drowning', '溺', '<img src=\"E6BABA.png\" />', 'drowning, water, water droplets, water pistol, weak, bow, ice, bow2, ice2', '13', '33', 'Weak people placed in the water start drowning. Get some strength in those arms and learn how to swim!', 'JH', '', 'デキ、ジョウ、ニョウ', 'いばり、おぼ.れる', NULL, NULL),
('1325', 'seethe', '沸', '<img src=\"E6B2B8.png\" />', 'seethe, water, water droplets, water pistol, dollar, bow, stick, stick2', '8', '33', 'Re CharleyGarrett: This liquid looks like ordinary water, but it will instantly seethe when it comes in contact with counterfeit dollar bills. The inventor must be rich (and probably has dollar signs in his eyes).', 'JH', '2', 'フツ', 'わ.く、わ.かす', NULL, NULL),
