('134', 'stream', '川', '<img src=\"E5B79D.png\" />', 'stream, flood', '3', '8', 'So as not to confuse this with river (#146) think of streamers falling down.', '1', '5', 'セン', 'かわ', NULL, NULL),
('1340', 'old man', '老', '<img src=\"E88081.png\" />', 'old man, old man, soil, dirt, ground, spoon, sitting on the ground', '6', '34', 'An old man, wondering what it´s like in a grave, sits in a freshly dug plot. When a gravekeeper mistakes him for dead and begins burying him with soil, the old man saves himself by flailing his walking stick in the air.', '4', '3', 'ロウ', 'お.いる、ふ.ける', NULL, NULL),
('1341', 'consider', '考', '<img src=\"E88083.png\" />', 'consider, old man, slingshot, catapult', '6', '34', 'Before shooting an old man with a slingshot, one shold carefully consider the possible consequences.', '2', '4', 'コウ', 'かんが.える、かんが.え', NULL, NULL),
('1342', 'filial piety', '孝', '<img src=\"E5AD9D.png\" />', 'filial piety, old man, child', '7', '34', 'This child has taken filial piety to the next level. He is actually carrying the old man on his shoulders.', '6', '', 'コウ、キョウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('1343', 'teach', '教', '<img src=\"E69599.png\" />', 'teach, filial piety, old man, child, taskmaster', '11', '34', 'In early Japan, filial piety was the cornerstone of education, and harsh taskmasters were employed to teach it.', '2', '4', 'キョウ', 'おし.える、おそ.わる', NULL, NULL),
('1344', 'torture', '拷', '<img src=\"E68BB7.png\" />', 'torture, finger, fingers, consider, old man, slingshot, catapult', '9', '34', 'In Torture 101 class they teach you to Consider the Fingers as the first part to inflict pain to. Then you can move on to other parts (like feet, groin, head, etc. etc. ; ) ).', 'JH', '1', 'ゴウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('1345', 'someone', '者', '<img src=\"E88085.png\" />', 'someone, puppet, sooty, old man, sun, day', '8', '34', 'I find the best way of memorizing this kanji is in conjunction with the Japanese compound for ninja: 忍者 -- i.e. someone who endures (see FRAME 597 for the kanji 忍). A 忍者 is not just a 身 (somebody), it´s 者 who can 忍 great 拷!', '3', '4', 'シャ', 'もの', NULL, NULL),
('1346', 'boil', '煮', '<img src=\"E785AE.png\" />', 'boil, someone, puppet, sooty, old man, sun, day, oven-fire, barbecue', '12', '34', 'I had a hard time with the next several frame numbers trying to use \"puppet.\" So i thought of \"voodoo doll\" but then found \"love doll\" (which is just a special type of puppet) fit well with these 8 frames. Observe: Here I am boiling my love doll over the flames to warm her up a bit...', 'JH', '1', 'シャ', 'に.る、-に、に.える、に.やす', NULL, NULL),
('1347', 'renowned', '著', '<img src=\"E89197.png\" />', 'renowned, flowers, someone, puppet, sooty, old man, sun, day', '11', '34', 'Here I am, putting a wreath of flowers on my love doll´s head and pretending she is someone of great renowned.', '6', '2', 'チョ、チャク', 'あらわ.す、いちじる.しい', NULL, NULL),
('1348', 'chopsticks', '箸', '<img src=\"E7AEB8.png\" />', 'chopsticks, bamboo, someone, puppet, sooty, old man, sun, day', '14', '34', 'Bamboo, lovedoll: At dinner, my lovedoll decided to eat her meal the Japanese way using chopsticks. But well, what a problems she had getting those bamboo shoots into her mouth (which should not be that difficult, I would say!).', 'JH', '', 'チョ、チャク', 'はし', NULL, NULL),
('1349', 'signature', '署', '<img src=\"E7BDB2.png\" />', 'signature, eye, cross-eyed, net, someone, puppet, sooty, old man, sun, day', '13', '34', 'Before giving your SIGNATURE to accept the LOVEDOLL, you should EYE over the LOVEDOLL for any damages, then give your SIGNATURE.', '6', '2', 'ショ', '', NULL, NULL),
('135', 'state', '州', '<img src=\"E5B79E.png\" />', 'state, stream, flood, drops', '6', '8', 'There were 3 little islands in the stream who all decided to set themselves up as independent states.', '3', '2', 'シュウ、ス', 'す', NULL, NULL),
