('1351', 'various', '諸', '<img src=\"E8ABB8.png\" />', 'various, say, words, keitai, mouth, someone, puppet, sooty, old man, sun, day', '15', '34', 'Because i get tired of saying the same old thing, I have lately been trying to use various terms of endearment to my love doll. I think she appreciates it too.', '6', '2', 'ショ', 'もろ', NULL, NULL),
('1352', 'boar', '猪', '<img src=\"E78CAA.png\" />', 'boar, pack of wild dogs, someone, puppet, sooty, old man, sun, day', '11', '34', 'My love doll is made of special pheremone impregnated vinyl. Unfortunately, a pack of wild dogs mistook her for a wild boar and tore her to pieces. Oh dear!', 'Nam', '1', 'チョ', 'い、いのしし', NULL, NULL),
('1353', 'strand', '渚', '<img src=\"E6B89A.png\" />', 'strand, water, water droplets, water pistol, someone, puppet, sooty, old man, sun, day', '11', '34', 'I was stranded on a desert island surrounded by water for hundreds of miles on end. I wasn´t upset though - I had my love doll! What a great strand of sand to be stranded on - just me and my love doll!', 'Nam', '1', 'ショ', 'なぎさ', NULL, NULL),
('1354', 'gamble', '賭', '<img src=\"E8B3AD.png\" />', 'gamble, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight, someone, puppet, sooty, old man, sun, day', '15', '34', 'When we gamble at the shell game, I always win against my love doll.', 'JH', '', 'ト', 'か.ける、かけ', NULL, NULL),
('1355', 'gorge', '峡', '<img src=\"E5B3A1.png\" />', 'gorge, mountain, scissors, husband, horns', '9', '34', 'A gorge is where God has cut into a mountain with a pair of scissors. (synewave,6-10-2006) http://www.travelblog.org/Photos/197361.html.', 'JH', '1', 'キョウ、コウ', 'はざま', NULL, NULL),
('1356', 'cramped', '狭', '<img src=\"E78BAD.png\" />', 'cramped, pack of wild dogs, scissors, husband, horns', '9', '34', 'A pack of wild dogs, waiting in a very cramped waiting room, to get their hair cut by Edward Scissors Hands, who is very popular.', 'JH', '1', 'キョウ、コウ', 'せま.い、せば.める、せば.まる、さ', NULL, NULL),
('1357', 'sandwiched', '挟', '<img src=\"E68C9F.png\" />', 'sandwiched, finger, fingers, scissors, husband, horns', '9', '34', '挟まる 【はさまる】 (v5r,vi) to get between; to be caught in; (P) Story: You know how in tokyo there are those really packed trains where train staff in gloves shove people in? Well imagine being sandwiched in so tight, that when the doors close, only your FINGERS are sticking out. The train staff have no choice... they must cut them off with SCISSORS =( snip snip..', 'JH', '2', 'キョウ、ショウ', 'はさ.む、はさ.まる、わきばさ.む、さしはさ.む', NULL, NULL),
('1358', 'cheek', '頬・頰', '<img src=\"E9A0AC.png\" />', 'cheek, scissors, husband, horns, head, page, one, ceiling, drop, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '15', '34', 'Your cheeks contain your jawbones, which are known as the \"scissors of the head.\".', 'JH', '', 'キョウ', 'ほお、ほほ', NULL, NULL),
('1359', 'chase', '追', '<img src=\"E8BFBD.png\" />', 'chase, maestro, road', '9', '34', 'Maestro, coattails flapping wildly, is being chased down the road by his fans.', '3', '3', 'ツイ', 'お.う', NULL, NULL),
('136', 'obey', '順', '<img src=\"E9A086.png\" />', 'obey, stream, flood, head, page, one, ceiling, drop, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '12', '8', 'Obey, Obey! says the brain-washing scientist as he sends a stream of orders to fill your head.', '4', '2', 'ジュン', '', NULL, NULL),
('1360', 'large hill', '阜', '<img src=\"E9989C.png\" />', 'large hill, maestro, ten, needle', '8', '34', 'The maestro lives on top of a large hill so that he can play music at over ten decibels without anyone giving a damn.', 'JH', '', 'フ、フウ', '', NULL, NULL),
