('1389', 'overdo', '過', '<img src=\"E9818E.png\" />', 'overdo, jawbone, joint, hood, mouth, road', '12', '34', 'Jaws XII~! Jaws strikes the highway! Man, they´re really overdoing it now.', '5', '3', 'カ', 'す.ぎる、-す.ぎる、-す.ぎ、す.ごす、あやま.つ、あやま.ち、よ.ぎる', NULL, NULL),
('139', 'eternity', '永', '<img src=\"E6B0B8.png\" />', 'eternity, drop, water', '5', '8', 'It would take an eternity to count all the drops of water.', '5', '2', 'エイ', 'なが.い', NULL, NULL),
('1390', 'Heights', '阪', '<img src=\"E998AA.png\" />', 'heights, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, anti-, demonstration, cliff, crotch', '7', '35', 'If you´re scared of Heights, you don´t want to stay at The Pinnacle; you are anti- The Pinnacle. Primitive: The Pinnacle is a dream-like gated community at the top of a mount. This allows for innumerable stories for all the kanji with this primitive since you have a whole city to work with. Also prevents confusion with \"mountain\".', 'JH', '', 'ハン', 'さか', NULL, NULL),
('1391', 'Africa', '阿', '<img src=\"E998BF.png\" />', 'africa, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, can, mouth, street, nail, spike', '8', '35', 'Can you see Africa from The Pinnacle? I can! I can!', 'Nam', '1', 'ア、オ', 'おもね.る', NULL, NULL),
('1392', 'occasion', '際', '<img src=\"E99A9B.png\" />', 'occasion, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, ritual, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, crotch, altar, show, two, small', '14', '35', 'Many rituals are practiced every day (blessing before meals, evening prayer, etc.) Only the peak rituals (wedding, Bar Mitzvah, etc.) qualify to be called an occasion.', '5', '3', 'サイ', 'きわ、-ぎわ', NULL, NULL),
('1393', 'hinder', '障', '<img src=\"E99A9C.png\" />', 'hinder, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, badge, vase, stand up, sunflower, early, sun, day, ten, needle', '14', '35', 'The officer at the gate to The Pinnacle with a giant badge sewn to his chest hinders all visitors. But not the handicapped. They´re hindered enough already. They´re given a badge and can pass right into The Pinnacle.', '6', '1', 'ショウ', 'さわ.る', NULL, NULL),
('1394', 'chink', '隙', '<img src=\"E99A99.png\" />', 'chink, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, small, little, sun, day, small2, little, 2', '13', '35', 'There was only one chink in his plan. Even standing atop the highest pinnacle, standing above even the sun, the little man was still just as little as when he was under the sun.', 'JH', '', 'ゲキ、キャク、ケキ', 'すき、す.く、す.かす、ひま', NULL, NULL),
('1395', 'follow', '随', '<img src=\"E99A8F.png\" />', 'follow, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, highwayman, possess, by one’s side, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, road', '12', '35', '[Image: Follow the ´Yellow-Brick Road´ to success] The pinnacle signifies your personal goal and destination. What you´re seeking to possess lies at the end of the yellow-brick road. You must follow the road to get what you want.', 'JH', '1', 'ズイ', 'まにまに、したが.う', NULL, NULL),
('1396', 'auxiliary', '陪', '<img src=\"E999AA.png\" />', 'obeisance, auxiliary, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, muzzle, vase, stand up, mouth', '11', '35', 'In case of emergency, The Pinnacle has auxiliary guard dogs, but they keep them muzzeled until they´re needed.', 'JH', '1', 'バイ', '', NULL, NULL),
('1397', 'sunshine', '陽', '<img src=\"E999BD.png\" />', 'sunshine, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, piggy bank, sun, day, piglets', '12', '35', 'A kid is perched on a pinnacle with his piggy bank. He uses the coins to catch the sunshine, and redirect it into people´s eyes, far below.', '3', '3', 'ヨウ', 'ひ', NULL, NULL),
('1398', 'line up', '陳', '<img src=\"E999B3.png\" />', 'exhibit, line up, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, east, tree, wood, sun, day', '11', '35', 'Every morning at The Pinnacle, the residents line upon the East side for morning stretches and leisure.', 'JH', '1', 'チン', 'ひ.ねる', NULL, NULL),
('1399', 'ward off', '防', '<img src=\"E998B2.png\" />', 'ward off, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, compass, direction', '7', '35', 'A giant compass is The Pinnacle´s self-defense system. It points in the direction of any invaders so the city is prepared well ahead to ward off the intruders.', '5', '2', 'ボウ', 'ふせ.ぐ', NULL, NULL),
('14', 'rice field', '田', '<img src=\"E794B0.png\" />', 'rice field, brains', '5', '1', 'A rice field divided into four parts.', '1', '4', 'デン', 'た', NULL, NULL),
('140', 'spring', '泉', '<img src=\"E6B389.png\" />', 'spring, white, dove, water', '9', '8', 'White is a symbol of purety, so white water is pure water, the precise definition of spring water.', '6', '2', 'セン', 'いずみ', NULL, NULL),
('1400', 'affixed', '附', '<img src=\"E99984.png\" />', 'affixed, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, adhere, sellotape, person, glue', '8', '35', 'A sign was AFFIXED on the PINNACLE of the Acropolis so that tourists would ADHERE to the rules.', 'JH', '1', 'フ', 'つ.ける、つ.く', NULL, NULL),
('1401', 'Inst.', '院', '<img src=\"E999A2.png\" />', 'Inst., pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, perfect, house, beginnings, two, human legs', '10', '35', 'The Institution of The Pinnacle is perfect in every way. It is the new House of God, his chosen city.', '3', '4', 'イン', '', NULL, NULL),
('1402', 'camp', '陣', '<img src=\"E999A3.png\" />', 'camp, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, car', '10', '35', 'Paparazzi make camp outside of The Pinnacle in their cars, waiting for the celebs to come out.', 'JH', '1', 'ジン', '', NULL, NULL),
('1403', 'regiment', '隊', '<img src=\"E99A8A.png\" />', 'regiment, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, animal horns, sow, pig, wart hog, regimental mascot', '12', '35', 'Every regiment of The Pinnacle´s army is lead by a Miss Piggy with a viking helmet on.', '4', '1', 'タイ', '', NULL, NULL),
('1404', 'crash', '墜', '<img src=\"E5A29C.png\" />', 'crash, regiment, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, animal horns, sow, pig, wart hog, regimental mascot, soil, dirt, ground', '15', '35', 'One of the members of our air force regiment has been shot down; he managed to safely eject, but his plane crashed into the ground.', 'JH', '1', 'ツイ', 'お.ちる、お.つ', NULL, NULL),
('1405', 'descend', '降', '<img src=\"E9998D.png\" />', 'descend, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, walking legs, sunglasses with one lens missing, monocle', '10', '35', 'Sunglasses-missing-one-lens is obviously the monocle. The proper, high-class way to descend The Pinnacle is wearing a monocle with your walking legs splayed to a full gentlemanly stride.', '6', '3', 'コウ、ゴ', 'お.りる、お.ろす、ふ.る、ふ.り、くだ.る、くだ.す', NULL, NULL),
('1406', 'story', '階', '<img src=\"E99A8E.png\" />', 'storey, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, all, compare, spoon, sitting on the ground, white, dove, spoon2, sitting on the ground2', '12', '35', 'All buildings of The Pinnacle are multi-storey. They don´t have much room, so they have to build up. It sucks when someone presses all the buttons on the elevator! You have to stop at each storey!', '3', '2', 'カイ', 'きざはし', NULL, NULL),
('1407', 'highness', '陛', '<img src=\"E9999B.png\" />', 'highness, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, compare, spoon, sitting on the ground, soil, dirt, ground, spoon2, sitting on the ground2', '10', '35', 'Your highness is the pinnacle of finesse compared to all of us commoners who are but like dirt on the ground.', '6', '1', 'ヘイ', '', NULL, NULL),
('1408', 'neighboring', '隣', '<img src=\"E99AA3.png\" />', 'neighbouring, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, shoeshine, rice, sunglasses, dancing legs, ballerina, evening', '16', '35', 'America thinks it is the pinnacle of the world, looking down on all neighboring countries through its mirrored, aviator sunglasses.', 'JH', '1', 'リン', 'とな.る、となり', NULL, NULL),
('1409', 'isolate', '隔', '<img src=\"E99A94.png\" />', 'isolate, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, tripod, one, ceiling, mouth, hood, human legs, street, nail, spike', '13', '35', 'The Pinnacle, to me, is a city that makes itself out to be perfect but is filled with dirty secrets that photographers are always trying to reveal (see dissolve (#1044) The city´s councilmen have isolated all professional photographers to make sure they don´t photograph these \"dirty secrets\". (which are up to your imagination).', 'JH', '1', 'カク', 'へだ.てる、へだ.たる', NULL, NULL),
('141', 'gland', '腺', '<img src=\"E885BA.png\" />', 'gland, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, spring, white, dove, water', '13', '8', 'A body part that acts like a spring for hormones is a gland.', 'JH', '', 'セン', '', NULL, NULL),
('1410', 'conceal', '隠', '<img src=\"E99AA0.png\" />', 'conceal, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, hideaway, claw, vulture, broom, heart', '14', '35', 'The wheat farmer´s heart is calm (#1147) about the eagle not stealing his crops because of the broom scarecrow. But he still conceals all his wheat at The Pinnacle in case anyone else trys to steal it.', 'JH', '1', 'イン、オン', 'かく.す、かく.し、かく.れる、かか.す、よ.る', NULL, NULL),
('1411', 'degenerate', '堕', '<img src=\"E5A095.png\" />', 'degenerate, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, possess, by one’s side, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, ground, soil, dirt, ground', '12', '35', 'Any attempt to possess the pinnacle will degenerate into a land (\"ground\") war.', 'JH', '1', 'ダ', 'お.ちる、くず.す、くず.れる', NULL, NULL),
('1412', 'collapse', '陥', '<img src=\"E999A5.png\" />', 'collapse, pinnacle, parthenon, acropolis, straight-jacket, bound up, olden times, old days, stick, sun, day', '10', '35', 'The Pinnacle is actually bound up by supports from olden times. Eventually, they give out, and the whole thing starts to collapse.', 'JH', '1', 'カン', 'おちい.る、おとしい.れる', NULL, NULL),
('1413', 'hole', '穴', '<img src=\"E7A9B4.png\" />', 'hole, house, eight', '5', '35', 'A black hole is a \"House of Infinity\". Infinity is of course represented by a sideways \"8\", but here we have a Japanese \"8\" instead.', '6', '1', 'ケツ', 'あな', NULL, NULL),
('1414', 'empty', '空', '<img src=\"E7A9BA.png\" />', 'empty, hole, house, human legs, craft', '8', '35', 'The craft of creating a black hole is in creating an emptiness which can attract things.', '1', '4', 'クウ', 'そら、あ.く、あ.き、あ.ける、から、す.く、す.かす、むな.しい', NULL, NULL),
('1415', 'withdraw', '控', '<img src=\"E68EA7.png\" />', 'withdraw, finger, fingers, empty, sky, hole, house, human legs, craft', '11', '35', 'With my fingers, I punch in my bank code and withdraw some money from my account. And now it´s empty again, as usual!', 'JH', '1', 'コウ', 'ひか.える、ひか.え', NULL, NULL),
('1416', 'stab', '突', '<img src=\"E7AA81.png\" />', 'stab, hole, house, human legs, large, St. Bernard', '8', '35', 'When you stab something you often leave a big hole.', 'JH', '3', 'トツ、カ', 'つ.く', NULL, NULL),
('1417', 'research', '究', '<img src=\"E7A9B6.png\" />', 'research, hole, house, human legs, nine, baseball', '7', '35', 'Most research scientists have 9 holes.....two nostrils, two ears, a mouth, and four eyes...... :-).', '3', '4', 'キュウ、ク', 'きわ.める', NULL, NULL),
('1418', 'plug up', '窒', '<img src=\"E7AA92.png\" />', 'plug up, hole, house, human legs, climax, wall, one, ceiling, elbow, soil, dirt, ground', '11', '35', 'Sticking a plug up your hole will lead to stronger climaxes.', 'JH', '1', 'チツ', '', NULL, NULL),
('1419', 'stealth', '窃', '<img src=\"E7AA83.png\" />', 'stealth, hole, house, human legs, cut, seven, sword, dagger', '9', '35', 'This more commonly means \"steal\", like how a thief cuts a hole to steal the jewels.', 'JH', '1', 'セツ', 'ぬす.む、ひそ.か', NULL, NULL),
('142', 'meadow', '原', '<img src=\"E58E9F.png\" />', 'meadow, cliff, spring, white, dove, small, little', '10', '8', 'Follow the springs down the cliff and you will find a nice meadow.', '2', '3', 'ゲン', 'はら', NULL, NULL),
('1420', 'cavern', '窟', '<img src=\"E7AA9F.png\" />', 'cavern, hole, house, human legs, yield, flag, exit', '13', '35', 'After Osama blew a hole in NY, the counterreaction forced him to yield and retreat into caverns.', 'JH', '', 'クツ、コツ', 'いわや、いはや、あな', NULL, NULL),
('1421', 'depression', '窪', '<img src=\"E7AAAA.png\" />', 'depression, hole, house, human legs, water, water droplets, water pistol, ivy, square jewel, soil, dirt, ground, soil2, dirt2, ground2', '14', '35', 'A depression is a hole in the ground. Water naturally collects there which provides moisture for vines to grow.', 'Nam', '', 'ワ、ア', 'くぼ.む、くぼ.み、くぼ.まる、くぼ', NULL, NULL),
('1422', 'squeeze', '搾', '<img src=\"E690BE.png\" />', 'squeeze, finger, fingers, tight, hole, house, human legs, saw', '13', '35', 'You have trouble squeezing your hand through the hole so you use a saw to enlarge it.', 'JH', '1', 'サク', 'しぼ.る', NULL, NULL),
('1423', 'kiln', '窯', '<img src=\"E7AAAF.png\" />', 'kiln, hole, house, human legs, sheep, oven-fire, barbecue', '15', '35', 'Be sure to put a hole in that ceramic sheep before you put it over the fire. Otherwise, it´ll just explode in the kiln. (If you´ve never done ceramics before, it´s important that the object have a hole in it, or this really will happen.).', 'JH', '1', 'ヨウ', 'かま', NULL, NULL),
('1424', 'hard up', '窮', '<img src=\"E7AAAE.png\" />', 'hard up, hole, house, human legs, somebody, nose, bow', '15', '35', 'Hard up = nothing but your body, living in a hole, with just a bow to hunt for your food.', 'JH', '1', 'キュウ、キョウ', 'きわ.める、きわ.まる、きわ.まり、きわ.み', NULL, NULL),
('1425', 'grope', '探', '<img src=\"E68EA2.png\" />', 'grope, finger, fingers, paper punch, Miss World, hole, house, human legs, tree, wood', '11', '35', 'A pictograph of a japanese schoolgirl getting groped by perverts on the train. The fingers of course, a crown (her too short skirt) and her legs below (which to be honest are pretty thick like tree trunks).', '6', '3', 'タン', 'さぐ.る、さが.す', NULL, NULL),
('1426', 'deep', '深', '<img src=\"E6B7B1.png\" />', 'deep, water, water droplets, water pistol, paper punch, Miss World, hole, house, human legs, tree, wood', '11', '35', 'If the groper´s \"tree\" goes up the girl´s miniskirt too deep, he´ll ejaculate fluid. (Sorry it´s kinda coarse but it works.).', '3', '3', 'シン', 'ふか.い、-ぶか.い、ふか.まる、ふか.める、み-', NULL, NULL),
('1427', 'hill', '丘', '<img src=\"E4B898.png\" />', 'hill, axe, one, floor', '5', '35', 'Excalibur is the sword planted in a rock. Lesser known AXCAHILLBUR is the axe planted on top of a hill.', 'JH', '1', 'キュウ', 'おか', NULL, NULL),
('1428', 'Point', '岳', '<img src=\"E5B2B3.png\" />', 'point, hill, axe, one, floor, mountain', '8', '35', 'A point is a extra little hill at the top of a mountain. We´ll call it ´Fireman´s Point´.', 'JH', '1', 'ガク', 'たけ', NULL, NULL),
('1429', 'soldier', '兵', '<img src=\"E585B5.png\" />', 'soldier, hill, axe, one, floor, animal legs, eight', '7', '35', 'Listen up soldiers! We´re going to take that hill. You are no longer men with human legs. You are voracious animals, with animal legs! Got it? Animal legs! Now take that hill!', '4', '2', 'ヘイ、ヒョウ', 'つわもの', NULL, NULL),
('143', 'petition', '願', '<img src=\"E9A198.png\" />', 'petition, meadow, cliff, white, dove, small, little, head, page, one, ceiling, drop, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '19', '8', 'Let´s petition to save that beautiful MEADOW from overdevelopment by signing on this PAGE.', '4', '3', 'ガン', 'ねが.う、-ねがい', NULL, NULL),
('1430', 'seacoast', '浜', '<img src=\"E6B59C.png\" />', 'seacoast, water, water droplets, water pistol, soldier, hill, axe, one, floor, animal legs, eight', '10', '35', 'Seacoast -> Coast Guard -> \"water soldiers\" lined up on the seacoast defending our shores.', 'JH', '1', 'ヒン', 'はま', NULL, NULL),
('1431', 'thread', '糸', '<img src=\"E7B3B8.png\" />', 'thread, spiderman', '6', '36', 'I also went with Spiderman. However, in the cases where this primitive appears under other primitives, as opposed to on the left (I think there are ~5 times in this chapter) I´ve opted to use a similar character: Venom. This helps keep the positioning clear, especially on such characters as dainty (#1363) and accumulate (#1364).', '1', '2', 'シ', 'いと', NULL, NULL),
('1432', 'weave', '織', '<img src=\"E7B994.png\" />', 'weave, thread, spiderman, kazoo, sound, vase, stand up, sun, day, fiesta', '18', '36', 'Spiderman weaves his way through the skyline while listening to his theme song on his ipod. It is played, of course, by kazoos.', '5', '1', 'ショク、シキ', 'お.る、お.り、おり、-おり、-お.り', NULL, NULL),
('1433', 'darning', '繕', '<img src=\"E7B995.png\" />', 'darning, thread, spiderman, virtuous, sheep, horns, mouth', '18', '36', 'After a day being virtuouos and keeping the city safe, Spiderman´s outfit is in need of some repair. Luckily, as he can shoot out threads darning is very easy for him to do.', 'JH', '1', 'ゼン', 'つくろ.う', NULL, NULL),
('1434', 'shrink', '縮', '<img src=\"E7B8AE.png\" />', 'shrink, thread, spiderman, inn, house, person, hundred, one, ceiling, white, dove', '17', '36', 'After spending the night at an inn, spider man discovered to his dismay that his costume had shrunk in the wash, and no longer fit!', '6', '1', 'シュク', 'ちぢ.む、ちぢ.まる、ちぢ.める、ちぢ.れる、ちぢ.らす', NULL, NULL),
('1435', 'luxuriant', '繁', '<img src=\"E7B981.png\" />', 'luxuriant, cleverness, reclining, lying down, mother, breasts, taskmaster, thread, spiderman', '16', '36', 'Important: Luxuriant does NOT mean luxurious, as the other stories indicate. Definition: abundant or lush in growth, as vegetation. When Venom realized he couldn´t beat Spider-Man in a fair fight, he showed his cleverness by spraying venom all over Spider-Man´s luxuriant garden.', 'JH', '1', 'ハン', 'しげ.る、しげ.く', NULL, NULL),
('1436', 'vertical', '縦', '<img src=\"E7B8A6.png\" />', 'vertical, thread, spiderman, accompany, Nelson, column, going, line, horns, mend', '16', '36', 'When Spider-man does his amazing vertical wall climbing, a throng of photographers accompanies him to get a good shot of the action.', '6', '1', 'ジュウ', 'たて', NULL, NULL),
('1437', 'fine', '緻', '<img src=\"E7B7BB.png\" />', '', '16', '36', 'THREAD, DOTH. fine THREADS DOTH make fine cloth. Think of a Shakespearean character stating this to someone else. Picture fine threads on one side of the picture and an aftershot of a fine cloth.', 'JH', '', 'チ', 'こまか.い', NULL, NULL),
('1438', 'line', '線', '<img src=\"E7B79A.png\" />', 'line, thread, spiderman, spring, white, dove, water', '15', '36', 'This kanji is used for train lines. Spiderman does a hot spring tour of Japan using the train lines. You can see the Spidey costume hanging on the washing line as he enjoys the onsen.', '2', '2', 'セン', 'すじ', NULL, NULL),
('1439', 'come apart at the seams', '綻', '<img src=\"E7B6BB.png\" />', 'come apart at the seams, thread, spiderman, determine, determined, house, mend', '14', '36', 'Even though his costume is coming apart at the seams as he chases the bad guys, Spiderman is still determined to catch them.', 'JH', '', 'タン', 'ほころ.びる', NULL, NULL),
('144', 'swim', '泳', '<img src=\"E6B3B3.png\" />', 'swim, water, water droplets, water pistol, eternity', '8', '8', 'With that much WATER (2 actually) you would need to swim for an ETERNITY.', '3', '3', 'エイ', 'およ.ぐ', NULL, NULL),
('1440', 'tighten', '締', '<img src=\"E7B7A0.png\" />', 'tighten, thread, spiderman, sovereign, vase, stand up, apron, crown, towel', '15', '36', 'The sovereign appears to be ruling, but in reality someone behind him (for instance his wife) has a thread around his throat, and if he dares to make a decision she doesn´t like, she starts pulling the thread and tightens it around his throat.', 'JH', '1', 'テイ', 'し.まる、し.まり、し.める、-し.め、-じ.め', NULL, NULL);
