('2124', 'groundbreaking', '墾', '<img src=\"E5A2BE.png\" />', 'groundbreaking, skunk, silver, soil, dirt, ground', '16', '53', 'It was the groundbreaking of the new farm, but there was an uninvited guest to the ceremony. It was a famous skunk, the one with the familiar silver stripe. The feet of the crowd rushing from the ceremony site churned up the soil very nicely. The ceremony was ruined but the groundbreaking was a great success.', 'JH', '1', 'コン', '', NULL, NULL),
('2125', 'countenance', '貌', '<img src=\"E8B28C.png\" />', 'countenance, skunk, badger, white, dove, human legs', '14', '53', 'Anyone who watched a looney tunes cartoon know those kind of scene : pepe embraces a poor kitty mistaken for a SKUNK and the smell of pepe make the unfortunate girl loose all countenance : she turns WHITE then runs as fast as her LEGS can carry her . So much for cat s dignity and countenance.', 'JH', '', 'ボウ、バク', 'かたち、かたどる', NULL, NULL),
('2126', 'excuse', '免', '<img src=\"E5858D.png\" />', 'excuse, village stocks, rabbit, bound up, human legs', '8', '53', 'Obviously this is the rabbit from Alice, excusing himself and rushing away on his legs, as he has a binding day schedule. This is at the same time an image, with bound=ears, day=head and legs are just legs. The image is used in rabbit (#2093).', 'JH', '1', 'メン', 'まぬか.れる、まぬが.れる', NULL, NULL),
