('338', 'cottage', '舎', '<img src=\"E8888E.png\" />', 'cottage, umbrella, earthenware jar, lidded crock, soil, dirt, ground, mouth', '8', '14', 'The cottage is so small - it has an umbrella for the roof; soil for the floor and room for only one mouth.', '5', '1', 'シャ、セキ', 'やど.る', NULL, NULL),
