('345', 'sell', '売', '<img src=\"E5A3B2.png\" />', 'sell, samurai, paper punch, Miss World, crown, human legs', '7', '14', 'The samurai happened to find an extra large crown that he wore as a belt on his waist, just above his legs. I wonder if he will sell it to me?', '2', '4', 'バイ', 'う.る、う.れる', NULL, NULL),
('346', 'study', '学', '<img src=\"E5ADA6.png\" />', 'study, schoolhouse, owl, crown, child', '8', '15', 'In the school house there are kids always studying. (BTW, atomiton, this is NOT 字).', '1', '5', 'ガク', 'まな.ぶ', NULL, NULL),
('347', 'memorize', '覚', '<img src=\"E8A69A.png\" />', 'memorize, schoolhouse, owl, crown, see, telescope, eye, human legs', '12', '15', 'In a schoolhouse in class: 1) you see something on the blackboard, then 2) you memorize it.', '4', '3', 'カク', 'おぼ.える、さ.ます、さ.める、さと.る', NULL, NULL),
