('351', 'breed', '牧', '<img src=\"E789A7.png\" />', 'breed, cow, taskmaster', '8', '15', 'Imagine a taskmaster giving a cow the command to \"start breeding, and start doing it now!\", except that the cow takes his advice a bit too literally and starts chasing the taskmaster to carry out this command! instead of finding another cow to breed with. Hence, you see the taskmaster running to the right, trying to stay ahead of the cow.', '4', '1', 'ボク', 'まき', NULL, NULL),
('352', 'aggression', '攻', '<img src=\"E694BB.png\" />', 'aggression, craft, taskmaster', '7', '15', 'Aggression is the craft of a good dominatrix.', 'JH', '1', 'コウ', 'せ.める', NULL, NULL),
('353', 'failure', '敗', '<img src=\"E69597.png\" />', 'failure, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight, taskmaster', '11', '15', 'If you end up in failure, you give money to the taskmaster to train you.', '4', '3', 'ハイ', 'やぶ.れる', NULL, NULL),
('354', 'a sheet of', '枚', '<img src=\"E69E9A.png\" />', 'sheet of…, tree, wood, taskmaster', '8', '15', 'The taskmaster is a strict bathroom monitor who hands out only one sheet of really rough, splintery toilet paper per person. You can see the wood fibers.', '6', '2', 'マイ、バイ', '', NULL, NULL),
('355', 'happenstance', '故', '<img src=\"E69585.png\" />', 'happenstance, old, tombstone, gravestone, church, ten, needle, mouth, taskmaster', '9', '15', 'An OLD TASKMASTER is no happenstance (coincidence). The older you get the more rigid in your ways.', '5', '1', 'コ', 'ゆえ、ふる.い、もと', NULL, NULL),
('356', 'awe', '敬', '<img src=\"E695AC.png\" />', 'awe, flowers, phrase, bound up, mouth, taskmaster', '12', '15', 'The flowery phrases of the schoolmaster held the students in awe.', '6', '2', 'ケイ、キョウ', 'うやま.う', NULL, NULL),
('357', 'say', '言', '<img src=\"E8A880.png\" />', 'say, words, keitai, mouth', '7', '15', 'A pictogram of someone saying a four letter word from their mouth after the censors have gotten a hold of it.', '2', '4', 'ゲン、ゴン', 'い.う、こと', NULL, NULL),
('358', 'admonish', '警', '<img src=\"E8ADA6.png\" />', 'admonish, awe, flowers, phrase, bound up, mouth, taskmaster, say, words, keitai, mouth, mouth2', '19', '15', 'To admonish is to enforce awe by means of words.', '6', '3', 'ケイ', 'いまし.める', NULL, NULL),
('359', 'plot', '計', '<img src=\"E8A888.png\" />', 'plot, say, words, keitai, mouth, ten, needle', '9', '15', 'A plot is a summary of a book that can be given in ten words.', '2', '4', 'ケイ', 'はか.る、はか.らう', NULL, NULL),
('36', 'oneself', '自', '<img src=\"E887AA.png\" />', 'oneself, drop, eye', '6', '3', 'Faced with his clone, our hero valiantly cut a mark on his forehead right above his eye so that his comrades could tell his true oneself from the enemy.', '2', '4', 'ジ、シ', 'みずか.ら、おの.ずから、おの.ずと', NULL, NULL),
('360', 'elucidate', '詮', '<img src=\"E8A9AE.png\" />', 'elucidate, say, words, keitai, mouth, whole, umbrella, king, jewel, ball', '13', '15', 'Words that tell you the results of the whole story really elucidate.', 'JH', '', 'セン', 'せん.ずる、かい、あき.らか', NULL, NULL),
('361', 'prison', '獄', '<img src=\"E78D84.png\" />', 'prison, pack of wild dogs, say, words, keitai, mouth, chihuahua, dog, large, drop', '14', '15', 'The wild dog family visits their cousin in prison. They exchange words over the interphone at the visiting booth.', 'JH', '1', 'ゴク', '', NULL, NULL),
('362', 'revise', '訂', '<img src=\"E8A882.png\" />', 'revise, say, words, keitai, mouth, street, nail, spike', '9', '15', 'Revise, revise and revise until you have all the words nailed down.', 'JH', '1', 'テイ', '', NULL, NULL),
('363', 'obituary', '訃', '<img src=\"E8A883.png\" />', '', '9', '15', 'Obituary. As a famous man lay dying, the media were already preparing the words of his obituary until a magician, with a wave of his wand, restored the man back to health.', 'JH', '', 'フ', 'しらせ<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>', NULL, NULL),
('364', 'chastise', '討', '<img src=\"E8A88E.png\" />', 'chastise, say, words, keitai, mouth, glue', '10', '15', 'I said some bad words, and my mother chastised me by washing my mouth out with glue instead of soap!', '6', '1', 'トウ', 'う.つ', NULL, NULL),
('365', 'instruction', '訓', '<img src=\"E8A893.png\" />', 'instruction, say, words, keitai, mouth, stream, flood', '10', '15', 'The best type of Japanese INSTRUCTION is full immersion, which consists of going to Japan and swimming in the stream of words that surrounds you every day.', '4', '2', 'クン、キン', 'おし.える、よ.む、くん.ずる', NULL, NULL),
('366', 'imperial edict', '詔', '<img src=\"E8A994.png\" />', 'imperial edict, say, words, keitai, mouth, summon, seduce, sword, dagger, mouth, mouth2', '12', '15', 'The mnemonic \"words to seduce the masses\" was just too vague and I kept forgetting it. So now instead I picture a seductive female reading aloud the imperial edict to the masses, thus \"seducing\" the masses.', 'JH', '1', 'ショウ', 'みことのり', NULL, NULL),
('367', 'packed', '詰', '<img src=\"E8A9B0.png\" />', 'packed, say, words, keitai, mouth, aerosol, good luck, samurai, mouth, mouth2', '13', '15', 'WORDS of GOOD LUCK are PACKED into fortune cookies.', 'JH', '2', 'キツ、キチ', 'つ.める、つ.め、-づ.め、つ.まる、つ.む', NULL, NULL),
('368', 'tale', '話', '<img src=\"E8A9B1.png\" />', 'tale, say, words, keitai, mouth, tongue, thousand, mouth, mouth2', '13', '15', 'Tales are always spoken, not written, and because of this, words fly out of your tongue, rather than your pen.', '2', '5', 'ワ', 'はな.す、はなし', NULL, NULL),
('369', 'recitation', '詠', '<img src=\"E8A9A0.png\" />', 'recitation, say, words, keitai, mouth, eternity, drop, water', '12', '15', 'Listening to the words in a recitation of Vogon poetry is worse than spending an eternity in hell. [Note: I assume those 2 reports are to warn against possible confusion with poem (#346) but how can you confuse Vogon poetry with an actual poem? Anyway, it´s the next frame, so it should be easy to keep them straight... Or maybe there´s a kanji for Vogon in RTK3?].', 'JH', '1', 'エイ', 'よ.む、うた.う', NULL, NULL),
('37', 'white', '白', '<img src=\"E799BD.png\" />', 'white, drop, sun, day', '5', '3', 'A white ray is a drop of sun.', '1', '5', 'ハク、ビャク', 'しろ、しら-、しろ.い', NULL, NULL),
