('511', 'briar', '茨', '<img src=\"E88CA8.png\" />', 'briar, flowers, next, ice, lack, yawn', '9', '18', 'To prevent animals from eating the beautiful flowers in your garden, the best thing to do is to plant briar bushes immediately next to them.', 'JH', '', 'シ、ジ', 'いばら、かや、くさぶき', NULL, NULL),
('512', 'assets', '資', '<img src=\"E8B387.png\" />', 'assets, next, ice, lack, yawn, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '13', '18', 'Assets are the next best thing to money.', '5', '3', 'シ', '', NULL, NULL),
('513', 'figure', '姿', '<img src=\"E5A7BF.png\" />', 'figure, next, ice, lack, yawn, woman', '9', '18', 'The next woman always has a better figure! Thinking like that, you´ll end up alone in an old folks home longing for the good old days!', '6', '1', 'シ', 'すがた', NULL, NULL),
('514', 'consult with', '諮', '<img src=\"E8ABAE.png\" />', 'consult with, say, words, keitai, mouth, next, ice, lack, yawn, mouth, mouth2', '16', '18', 'Having a word with the next mouth over, like a neighbor, is usually a good way to consult with somebody for cheap. Because, you know, actual consultants charge huge sums.', 'JH', '1', 'シ', 'はか.る', NULL, NULL),
('515', 'compensation', '賠', '<img src=\"E8B3A0.png\" />', 'compensation, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight, muzzle, vase, stand up, mouth', '15', '19', 'Compensation is money you give to someone to shut them up (i.e. muzzle their mouth).', 'JH', '1', 'バイ', '', NULL, NULL),
('516', 'cultivate', '培', '<img src=\"E59FB9.png\" />', 'cultivate, soil, dirt, ground, muzzle, vase, stand up, mouth', '11', '19', 'To cultivate the land is to tame it, control it. In short, you muzzle it´s unruly, chaotic nature.', 'JH', '1', 'バイ', 'つちか.う', NULL, NULL),
('517', 'divide', '剖', '<img src=\"E58996.png\" />', 'divide, muzzle, vase, stand up, mouth, sword, sabre, saber', '10', '19', 'When you DIVIDE someone, there is sure to be a lot of screaming. That´s why you should use a MUZZLE before using the SABER.', 'JH', '1', 'ボウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('518', 'sound', '音', '<img src=\"E99FB3.png\" />', 'sound, vase, stand up, sun, day, tongue wagging', '9', '19', 'If you were standing on the sun, believe me, you´d be making sound.', '1', '4', 'オン、イン、ノン', 'おと、ね', NULL, NULL),
('519', 'darkness', '暗', '<img src=\"E69A97.png\" />', 'darkness, sun, day, sound, vase, stand up, sun, day, sun2, day2', '13', '19', 'Picture the sun exploding - there would be a gigantic noise and then...nothing. Everything would plunge into darkness.', '3', '3', 'アン', 'くら.い、くら.む、くれ.る', NULL, NULL),
('52', 'eminent', '卓', '<img src=\"E58D93.png\" />', 'eminent, magic wand, augury, divinging rod, sunflower, sun, day, ten, needle', '8', '3', 'The most eminent magician is he who learned to use his magic wand early in life.', 'JH', '1', 'タク', '', NULL, NULL),
('520', 'rhyme', '韻', '<img src=\"E99FBB.png\" />', 'rhyme, sound, vase, stand up, sun, day, employee, mouth, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '19', '19', 'What is a RHYME but some SOUND that EMPLOYEES say to get them through work.', 'JH', '1', 'イン', '', NULL, NULL),
('521', 'discriminating', '識', '<img src=\"E8AD98.png\" />', 'discriminating, say, words, keitai, mouth, kazoo, sound, vase, stand up, sun, day, fiesta', '19', '19', 'Words are difficult to discriminate/discern from sounds in the middle of a fiesta.', '5', '3', 'シキ', 'し.る、しる.す', NULL, NULL),
('522', 'mirror', '鏡', '<img src=\"E98FA1.png\" />', 'mirror, metal, gold, mirror, vase, stand up, sun, day, human legs', '19', '19', 'Mirror should suggest vanity. Imagine a spoiled girl who gets her parents to buy her a Golden mirror so she can stand in front of it all day vainly admiring her lovely human legs.', '4', '1', 'キョウ、ケイ', 'かがみ', NULL, NULL),
('523', 'boundary', '境', '<img src=\"E5A283.png\" />', 'boundary, soil, dirt, ground, mirror, vase, stand up, sun, day, human legs', '14', '19', 'In the dense cities of Japan even a small garden is a luxury. In this house, the owner has put mirrors on the boundary of his land so it feels much bigger.', '5', '2', 'キョウ、ケイ', 'さかい', NULL, NULL),
('524', 'deceased', '亡', '<img src=\"E4BAA1.png\" />', 'deceased, perish, top hat, fishhook', '3', '19', 'The top hat hanging on a hook belonged to the now deceased Charlie Chaplin.', '6', '3', 'ボウ、モウ', 'な.い、な.き-、ほろ.びる、ほろ.ぶ、ほろ.ぼす', NULL, NULL),
('525', 'blind', '盲', '<img src=\"E79BB2.png\" />', 'blind, deceased, perish, top hat, fishhook, eye', '8', '19', 'Deceased eyes! Easy ;).', 'JH', '1', 'モウ', 'めくら', NULL, NULL),
('526', 'delusion', '妄', '<img src=\"E5A684.png\" />', 'delusion, deceased, perish, top hat, fishhook, woman', '6', '19', 'I had a problem with remembering that \"deceased\" went over the \"woman\". So, here´s my story: The delusional woman was carrying her deceased husband on her back.', 'JH', '1', 'モウ、ボウ', 'みだ.りに', NULL, NULL),
('527', 'laid waste', '荒', '<img src=\"E88D92.png\" />', 'laid waste, wreath, flowers, deceased, perish, top hat, fishhook, stream, flood', '9', '19', 'After Godzilla laid waste to the city, the survivors put some flowers on the bodies of the deceased and floated their bodies down the stream.', 'JH', '2', 'コウ', 'あら.い、あら-、あ.れる、あ.らす、-あ.らし、すさ.む', NULL, NULL),
('528', 'ambition', '望', '<img src=\"E69C9B.png\" />', 'ambition, deceased, perish, top hat, fishhook, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, king, jewel, ball', '11', '19', 'You´re dead meat, buddy, my ambition is to be king.', '4', '3', 'ボウ、モウ', 'のぞ.む、もち', NULL, NULL),
('529', 'direction', '方', '<img src=\"E696B9.png\" />', 'direction, compass, direction', '4', '19', 'Note: The primitives are top hat and bound up. Compare ten thousand (#64). Story: A rich man wearing a top hat and bound up from head to toe hobbles up to you and asks for directions to the nearest police station because he just escaped from his kidnappers.', '2', '4', 'ホウ', 'かた、-かた、-がた', NULL, NULL),
('53', 'morning', '朝', '<img src=\"E69C9D.png\" />', 'morning, mist, ten, needle, early, sun, day, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, ten2, needle2', '12', '3', 'There is mist as the moon fades away in the morning.', '2', '4', 'チョウ', 'あさ', NULL, NULL),
