('543', 'east', '東', '<img src=\"E69DB1.png\" />', 'east, sun, day, tree, wood', '8', '19', 'Traditionally seen as a pictograph of the sun rising behind a tree.', '2', '5', 'トウ', 'ひがし', NULL, NULL),
('544', 'ridgepole', '棟', '<img src=\"E6A39F.png\" />', 'ridgepole, tree, wood, east, tree, wood, sun, day, tree2, wood2', '12', '19', 'Feng Shui states that the ridgepole of a house should be made of wood and face east.', 'JH', '1', 'トウ', 'むね、むな-', NULL, NULL),
('545', 'frozen', '凍', '<img src=\"E5878D.png\" />', 'frozen, ice, east, tree, wood, sun, day', '10', '19', 'Eastern Siberia is often frozen by ice. According to wikipedia, Yakutia (in Eastern Siberia) holds the record as the coldest town on Earth. Check it out yourself...it made it stick for me!', 'JH', '2', 'トウ', 'こお.る、こご.える、こご.る、い.てる、し.みる', NULL, NULL),
('546', 'pregnancy', '妊', '<img src=\"E5A68A.png\" />', 'pregnancy, woman, porter, drop, samurai', '7', '19', 'A pregnant woman is a porter of her child.', 'JH', '1', 'ニン、ジン', 'はら.む、みごも.る', NULL, NULL),
('547', 'courts', '廷', '<img src=\"E5BBB7.png\" />', 'courts, porter, drop, samurai, stretch', '7', '19', 'A porter has run away from his master. His punishment is to be stretched out on the rack. So say the courts in this barbaric time.', 'JH', '1', 'テイ', '', NULL, NULL),
('548', 'dye', '染', '<img src=\"E69F93.png\" />', 'dye, water, water droplets, water pistol, nine, baseball, tree, wood', '9', '20', 'To make this dye, I used water and the barks of nine different trees.', '6', '1', 'セン', 'そ.める、-ぞ.め、-ぞめ、そ.まる、し.みる、-じ.みる、し.み、-し.める', NULL, NULL),
('549', 'burn', '燃', '<img src=\"E78783.png\" />', 'burn, fire, sort of thing, moon, crescent moon, month, flesh, part of the body, chihuahua, dog, large, drop, oven-fire, barbecue, fire2', '16', '20', 'Any sort of thing can burn in the fire.', '5', '2', 'ネン', 'も.える、も.やす、も.す', NULL, NULL),
('55', 'only', '只', '<img src=\"E58FAA.png\" />', 'only, mouth, animal legs, eight', '5', '4', 'Imagine an animal with only a mouth and legs.', 'Nam', '1', 'シ', 'ただ', NULL, NULL),
('550', 'V.I.P.', '賓', '<img src=\"E8B393.png\" />', 'V.I.P., house, one, ceiling, few, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '15', '20', 'This house is reserved to V.I.P. only. If you are not one of the few with enough money to call you that way, keep out!', 'JH', '1', 'ヒン', '', NULL, NULL),
('551', 'year-end', '歳', '<img src=\"E6ADB3.png\" />', 'year end, stop, footprint, one, little, small, march', '13', '20', 'Santa had to put his foot down to stop a march of little guys, namely elves. They were protesting the harsh treatment they get every year-end when Santa asks them to step up toy production for the holiday season.', 'JH', '3', 'サイ、セイ', 'とし、とせ、よわい', NULL, NULL),
('552', 'prefecture', '県', '<img src=\"E79C8C.png\" />', 'prefecture, eye, fishhook, small, little', '9', '20', '<span style=\" font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; \">In Japanese this is KEN, as in Barbie´s boyfriend. He has lovely blue&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style: normal; \">eyes</span><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; \">, a girlfriend who is as thin as a straightened out&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style: normal; \">fish hook</span><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; \">. But, down where it counts, he has very&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style: normal; \">little</span><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; \">&nbsp;to show...</span></span>', '3', '2', 'ケン', 'か.ける', NULL, NULL),
('553', 'horse chestnut', '栃', '<img src=\"E6A083.png\" />', 'horse chestnut, tree, wood, Wimbledon, cliff, ten thousand, one, bound up', '9', '20', 'There are a bunch of HORSE CHESTNUT TREES on top of this CLIFF above the beach. Chestnuts keep rolling off the cliff and falling on people´s heads. So far TEN THOUSAND people have been killed by falling chestnuts, and the Japanese government still ain´t did shit about it.', 'JH', '', '', 'とち', NULL, NULL),
('554', 'ground', '地', '<img src=\"E59CB0.png\" />', 'ground, soil, dirt, ground, scorpion', '6', '21', 'Picture the ground as an extent of soil where scorpions are buried like land mines. Imagine a sign post saying ´no trespassing, scorpion mines´ if that helps, and how it is dangerous to walk there.', '2', '4', 'チ、ジ', '', NULL, NULL),
('555', 'pond', '池', '<img src=\"E6B1A0.png\" />', 'pond, water, water droplets, water pistol, scorpion', '6', '21', 'Remember the story of the scorpion that begged the turtle for a ride across the pond? Halfway across the water, the scorpion stung the turtle on the neck and they both sank to the bottom.', '2', '2', 'チ', 'いけ', NULL, NULL),
('556', 'insect', '虫', '<img src=\"E899AB.png\" />', 'insect, in, stick, mouth', '6', '21', 'I see the bottom of this kanji as an arm, and the top is an insect biting into the arm, sucking some blood.', '1', '2', 'チュウ、キ', 'むし', NULL, NULL),
('557', 'lightning bug', '蛍', '<img src=\"E89B8D.png\" />', 'lightning-bug, schoolhouse, owl, crown, insect', '11', '21', 'Bugs have to go to school to learn how to become lightning bugs. Only the brightest bugs graduate to become lightning bugs.', 'JH', '1', 'ケイ', 'ほたる', NULL, NULL),
('558', 'snake', '蛇', '<img src=\"E89B87.png\" />', 'snake, insect, wind chimes, house, spoon, sitting on the ground', '11', '21', 'A snake eats insects and he does that outside, while we eat another snake in the house and preferably with a spoon.', 'JH', '1', 'ジャ、ダ、イ、ヤ', 'へび', NULL, NULL),
('559', 'rainbow', '虹', '<img src=\"E899B9.png\" />', 'rainbow, insect, craft', '9', '21', 'Little is it known that a rainbow is actually created by insects of different colours flying in formation, a craft they have perfected to create the rainbows we see today.', 'JH', '1', 'コウ', 'にじ', NULL, NULL),
('56', 'shellfish', '貝', '<img src=\"E8B29D.png\" />', 'shellfish, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '7', '4', 'Eye thought I saw a shellfish legging it down the beach!', '1', '2', 'バイ', 'かい', NULL, NULL),
('560', 'butterfly', '蝶', '<img src=\"E89DB6.png\" />', 'butterfly, insect, Tarzan, generation, tree, wood', '15', '21', 'A butterfly is an insect that appears after spending a generation on a tree as a cocoon.', 'Nam', '1', 'チョウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('561', 'single', '独', '<img src=\"E78BAC.png\" />', 'single, pack of wild dogs, insect', '9', '21', 'The bachelor´s apartment looked like it had been attacked by a pack of wild dogs. There were even insects in the kitchen. No wonder he´s single!', '5', '1', 'ドク、トク', 'ひと.り', NULL, NULL),
('562', 'silkworm', '蚕', '<img src=\"E89A95.png\" />', 'silkworm, heavens, insect', '10', '21', 'There are no insects in heaven - well, that is, except for silkworms. What, do you expect Jesus to import his fancy robes from China?', '6', '1', 'サン、テン', 'かいこ、こ', NULL, NULL),
('563', 'wind', '風', '<img src=\"E9A2A8.png\" />', 'wind, gnats, drop, insect', '9', '21', 'They say that when an INSECT flaps its wings even the single DROP of WIND that it creates is sometimes enough to create a hurricane on the other side of the Earth.', '2', '4', 'フウ、フ', 'かぜ、かざ-、-かぜ', NULL, NULL),
('564', 'self', '己', '<img src=\"E5B7B1.png\" />', 'self, snake, self', '3', '21', 'This kanji looks like the \"s\" of \"self\", looking at its own reflection in a mirror (reversed sideways), as if pondering about his \"self\".', '6', '1', 'コ、キ', 'おのれ、つちのと、な', NULL, NULL),
('565', 'rouse', '起', '<img src=\"E8B5B7.png\" />', 'rouse, run, soil, dirt, ground, mend, snake, self', '10', '21', 'Be careful when you´re RUNNING through the jungle, because you might step on and ROUSE a sleeping SNAKE. Then you´ll have to RUN like hell before it bites you!', '3', '4', 'キ', 'お.きる、お.こる、お.こす、おこ.す、た.つ', NULL, NULL),
('566', 'queen', '妃', '<img src=\"E5A683.png\" />', 'queen, woman, snake, self', '6', '21', 'Cleopatra.', 'JH', '1', 'ヒ', 'きさき', NULL, NULL),
('567', 'reformation', '改', '<img src=\"E694B9.png\" />', 'reformation, snake, self, taskmaster', '7', '21', 'The taskmaster of Slytherin ( wizardry house symbolized by a snake ) plans a reformation of Hogwarts, disallowing the study of magic to all muggle-born. こわいですね！.', '4', '2', 'カイ', 'あらた.める、あらた.まる', NULL, NULL),
('568', 'scribe', '記', '<img src=\"E8A898.png\" />', 'scribe, say, words, keitai, mouth, snake, self', '10', '21', 'A scribe writes down the words spoken by a snake (i.e. a lawyer).', '2', '3', 'キ', 'しる.す', NULL, NULL),
('569', 'wrap', '包', '<img src=\"E58C85.png\" />', 'wrap, bound up, snake, self', '5', '21', 'The snake bound up its prey by wrapping his body around it.', '4', '2', 'ホウ', 'つつ.む、くる.む', NULL, NULL),
('57', 'pop song', '唄', '<img src=\"E59484.png\" />', 'pop song, mouth, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '10', '4', 'The new generation of pop songs have no depth. They just mouth empty lyrics to get money. Not like the pop songs of my day.', 'JH', '1', 'バイ', 'うた、うた.う', NULL, NULL),
('570', 'placenta', '胞', '<img src=\"E8839E.png\" />', 'placenta, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, wrap, bound up, snake, self', '9', '21', 'Imagine a newborn baby, fresh out of the womb, being entirely wrapped by the long piece of flesh, called a placenta, that once fed him.', 'JH', '1', 'ホウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('571', 'cannon', '砲', '<img src=\"E7A0B2.png\" />', 'cannon, stone, rock, wrap, bound up, snake, self', '10', '21', 'Primitive cannons fired stones wrapped with poisonous snakes.', 'JH', '1', 'ホウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('572', 'bubble', '泡', '<img src=\"E6B3A1.png\" />', 'bubbles, water, water droplets, water pistol, wrap, bound up, snake, self', '8', '21', 'When water forms a bubble, it wraps a pocket of air.', 'JH', '1', 'ホウ', 'あわ', NULL, NULL),
