('641', 'selfish', '恣', '<img src=\"E681A3.png\" />', '', '10', '22', 'A selfish person doesn\'t care about the next person\'s heart, only their own.', 'JH', '', 'シ', 'ほしいまま', NULL, NULL),
('642', 'endure', '忍', '<img src=\"E5BF8D.png\" />', 'endure, blade, sword, dagger, drop, heart', '7', '22', 'A ninja must be able to endure the pain of clinging to a ceiling, motionless, for hours at a time, waiting for just the right moment to drop down and thrust the blade of his sword into the hearts of his enemies. By the way, this character is used in the compound 忍者 (ninja) which is why I choose to use ninja as its primitive meaning.', 'JH', '1', 'ニン', 'しの.ぶ、しの.ばせる', NULL, NULL),
('643', 'acknowledge', '認', '<img src=\"E8AA8D.png\" />', 'acknowledge, say, words, keitai, mouth, endure, blade, sword, dagger, drop, heart', '14', '22', 'You are given a speech about some serious mistakes of yours, and you have to endure the whole thing, because all you can do is acknowledge.', '6', '3', 'ニン', 'みと.める、したた.める', NULL, NULL),
('644', 'mourning', '忌', '<img src=\"E5BF8C.png\" />', 'mourning, snake, self, heart', '7', '22', 'Remember the tale of Cleopatra? She was MOURNING the loss of her Marc Antony, so she placed the asp SNAKE to her HEART.', 'JH', '1', 'キ', 'い.む、い.み、い.まわしい', NULL, NULL),
('645', 'intention', '志', '<img src=\"E5BF97.png\" />', 'intention, samurai, heart', '7', '22', 'A samurai´s intentions always come from the heart.', '5', '1', 'シ、シリング', 'こころざ.す、こころざし', NULL, NULL),
('646', 'document', '誌', '<img src=\"E8AA8C.png\" />', 'document, say, words, keitai, mouth, intention, samurai, heart', '14', '22', 'A will is an important document that contains your final word on how you intend to distribute your assets.', '6', '2', 'シ', '', NULL, NULL),
('647', 'wick', '芯', '<img src=\"E88AAF.png\" />', 'wick, flowers, heart', '7', '22', 'My favorite are heart shaped candles that smell like sweet flowers. The trick is to find one with a thick wick, they give off the most flower scent (but burn the quickest).', 'JH', '', 'シン', '', NULL, NULL),
('648', 'loyalty', '忠', '<img src=\"E5BFA0.png\" />', 'loyalty, in, stick, mouth, heart', '8', '22', 'Their true loyalty exists in the middle of their hearts.', '6', '1', 'チュウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('649', 'shish kebab', '串', '<img src=\"E4B8B2.png\" />', 'shish kebab, kebab, in, stick, mouth, mouth2', '7', '22', 'Naka naka , \"who´s there?\" shish kebab .... \"shish kebab who?\".', 'JH', '', 'カン、ケン、セン', 'くし、つらぬ.く', NULL, NULL),
('65', 'stubborn', '頑', '<img src=\"E9A091.png\" />', 'stubborn, beginning, two, human legs, head, page, one, ceiling, drop, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '13', '4', 'A stubborn person in the beginning gets something into their head and can´t change their mind.', 'JH', '1', 'ガン', 'かたく', NULL, NULL),
('650', 'afflicted', '患', '<img src=\"E682A3.png\" />', 'afflicted, kebab, in, stick, mouth, heart, mouth2', '11', '22', 'A person who is afflicted with the vampire disease can only be killed with a sheesh-kebab through the heart.', 'JH', '2', 'カン', 'わずら.う', NULL, NULL),
('651', 'think', '思', '<img src=\"E6809D.png\" />', 'think, rice field, brains, heart', '9', '22', 'Think with your brain NOT your heart.', '2', '4', 'シ', 'おも.う、おもえら.く、おぼ.す', NULL, NULL),
('652', 'grace', '恩', '<img src=\"E681A9.png\" />', 'grace, cause, pent in, large, St. Bernard, heart', '10', '22', 'Grace here is a favor freely bestowed, like a good deed. So to remember this kanji, go to the local shelter, find a big dog pent up in a small cage and adopt him. That will cause a warm feeling in your heart!', '5', '1', 'オン', '', NULL, NULL),
('653', 'apply', '応', '<img src=\"E5BF9C.png\" />', 'apply, cave, heart', '7', '22', 'In the videogame Zelda, Link enters a CAVE to visit a fairy that will APPLY magic to fill his HEART containers.', '5', '1', 'オウ、ヨウ、ノウ', 'あた.る、まさに、こた.える', NULL, NULL),
('654', 'idea', '意', '<img src=\"E6848F.png\" />', 'idea, sound, vase, stand up, sun, day, heart', '13', '22', 'When you get a good IDEA you get excited and you can hear the SOUND of your HEART, it´s pounding so hard.', '3', '4', 'イ', '', NULL, NULL),
('655', 'cowardice', '臆', '<img src=\"E88786.png\" />', 'cowardice, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, idea, sound, vase, stand up, sun, day, heart', '17', '22', 'Cowardice is the situation where you get the thought that maybe running away and saving your flesh is a good idea.', 'JH', '', 'オク、ヨク', 'むね、おくする', NULL, NULL),
('656', 'concept', '想', '<img src=\"E683B3.png\" />', 'concept, inter milan, inter, tree, wood, eye, heart', '13', '22', 'The concept of love is basically two hearts inter-acting as one.', '3', '3', 'ソウ、ソ', 'おも.う', NULL, NULL),
('657', 'breath', '息', '<img src=\"E681AF.png\" />', 'breath, nose, drop, eye, heart', '10', '22', 'Your breath brings oxygen in through your nose which is then pumped around your body by your heart.', '3', '3', 'ソク', 'いき', NULL, NULL),
('658', 'recess', '憩', '<img src=\"E686A9.png\" />', 'recess, tongue, thousand, mouth, nose, drop, eye, heart', '16', '22', 'Recess to me is a school break. At recess some kiddies are comparing their latest body piercings. Tongues and noses are nothing special. The new cool is to have your heart done!', 'JH', '1', 'ケイ', 'いこ.い、いこ.う', NULL, NULL),
('659', 'favor', '恵', '<img src=\"E681B5.png\" />', 'favor, ten, needle, rice field, brains, heart', '10', '22', 'Too easy. Imagine the Wizard of OZ. There, the three heroes asked the Wizard for three FAVORS: the lion wanted courage of TEN men, the scarecrow wanted a BRAIN, and the tin man wanted a HEART. Ok, the lion bit is stretching but you have it memorized now, so who cares?', 'JH', '1', 'ケイ、エ', 'めぐ.む、めぐ.み', NULL, NULL),
('66', 'mediocre', '凡', '<img src=\"E587A1.png\" />', 'mediocre, drop, wind', '3', '4', 'A drop of breeze is naught but a mediocre wind.', 'JH', '1', 'ボン、ハン', 'およ.そ、おうよ.そ、すべ.て', NULL, NULL),
('660', 'fear', '恐', '<img src=\"E68190.png\" />', 'fear, barge, craft, mediocre, drop, wind, heart', '10', '22', 'If your heart surgeon is mediocre in his craft, you have plenty of reason to fear. (\"Oops, I think I left my scissors in there\").', 'JH', '3', 'キョウ', 'おそ.れる、おそ.る、おそ.ろしい、こわ.い、こわ.がる', NULL, NULL),
('661', 'beguile', '惑', '<img src=\"E68391.png\" />', 'beguile, a, pope, fiesta, mouth, one, floor, heart', '12', '22', 'She was beguiled/mislead by his charm: at the party he kissed her on the mouth, they did it on the floor and thus he stole her heart. Poor girl!', 'JH', '1', 'ワク', 'まど.う', NULL, NULL),
('662', 'emotion', '感', '<img src=\"E6849F.png\" />', 'emotion, march, mouth, heart', '13', '22', 'Emotion is a march of mouths inside your heart telling you what to feel.', '3', '3', 'カン', '', NULL, NULL),
('663', 'melancholy', '憂', '<img src=\"E68682.png\" />', 'melancholy, summer, head, page, crown, heart, walking legs', '15', '22', 'Melancholy makes me think of Hamlet cause he was so ´emo´. In order to play up his feelings he bares his head and holds his crown over his heart then walks (on walking legs) around the palace making everyone see how melancholy he is. What a wuss.', 'JH', '1', 'ユウ', 'うれ.える、うれ.い、う.い、う.き', NULL, NULL),
('664', 'widow', '寡', '<img src=\"E5AFA1.png\" />', 'widow, house, head, page, animal legs, eight, sword, dagger', '14', '22', 'The new widow sits in the house, her head in her lap (the extended stroke), her dagger in her husband.', 'JH', '1', 'カ', '', NULL, NULL),
('665', 'busy', '忙', '<img src=\"E5BF99.png\" />', 'busy, Freud, state of mind, deceased, perish, top hat, fishhook', '6', '22', 'Busy (as in \"occupied\") means a state of mind where all other thoughts are perished.', 'JH', '3', 'ボウ、モウ', 'いそが.しい、せわ.しい、おそ.れる、うれえるさま', NULL, NULL),
('666', 'ecstasy', '悦', '<img src=\"E682A6.png\" />', 'ecstasy, Freud, state of mind, devil, horns, elder brother, teenager, mouth, human legs', '10', '22', 'ECSTASY alters our STATE OF MIND and makes us DEVILS.', 'JH', '1', 'エツ', 'よろこ.ぶ、よろこ.ばす', NULL, NULL),
('667', 'constancy', '恒', '<img src=\"E68192.png\" />', 'constancy, Freud, state of mind, span, one, ceiling, sun, day, one, floor, one', '9', '22', 'Constancy is holding the same state of mind over a long span of time. (tweaking PepeSeco and mspertus).', 'JH', '1', 'コウ', 'つね、つねに', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `kanjis` (`ID_Kanji`, `K_Keyword`, `K_Kanji`, `K_StrokeDiagram`, `K_Constituent`, `K_StrokeCount`, `K_LessonNo`, `K_Story`, `K_JouYou`, `K_JLPT`, `K_OnYomi`, `K_KunYomi`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
('668', 'lament', '悼', '<img src=\"E682BC.png\" />', 'lament, Freud, state of mind, eminent, magic wand, augury, sun, day, ten, needle', '11', '22', 'When the world´s most eminent magician died, everyone´s state of mind became that of lamentation. He was buried with his famous sun-flower wand in his hand.', 'JH', '1', 'トウ', 'いた.む', NULL, NULL),
('669', 'enlightenment', '悟', '<img src=\"E6829F.png\" />', 'enlightenment, Freud, state of mind, I, five, mouth', '10', '22', 'Enlightenment is a state of mind that goes beyond the five senses.', 'JH', '1', 'ゴ', 'さと.る', NULL, NULL),
('67', 'defeat', '負', '<img src=\"E8B2A0.png\" />', 'defeat, bound up, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '9', '4', 'Tied up, the shellfish had to accept defeat!', '3', '3', 'フ', 'ま.ける、ま.かす、お.う', NULL, NULL),
('670', 'dreadful', '怖', '<img src=\"E68096.png\" />', 'dreadful, Freud, state of mind, linen, by one’s side, towel', '8', '22', 'Someone in a dreadful state of mind has crawled into his bed and is hiding under the sheets (linens).', 'JH', '3', 'フ、ホ', 'こわ.い、こわ.がる、お.じる、おそ.れる', NULL, NULL),
('671', 'disconcerted', '慌', '<img src=\"E6858C.png\" />', 'disconcerted, Freud, state of mind, laid waste, wreath, flowers, deceased, perish, top hat, fishhook, stream, flood', '12', '22', '(re: wazzab) The state of mind of the people of New Orleans as they examined their city´s concert hall laid waste can best described as disconcerted.', 'JH', '', 'コウ', 'あわ.てる、あわ.ただしい', NULL, NULL),
('672', 'repent', '悔', '<img src=\"E68294.png\" />', 'repent, Freud, state of mind, every, reclining, lying down, mother, breasts', '9', '22', 'For all have sinned... so everyone´s state of mind should be to repent.', 'JH', '1', 'カイ', 'く.いる、く.やむ、くや.しい', NULL, NULL),
('673', 'hate', '憎', '<img src=\"E6868E.png\" />', 'hate, Freud, state of mind, increase, formerly, horns, rice field, brains, sun, day', '14', '22', 'Like the saying goes, Hate just begets Hate. A state of mind that just increases and increases until it explodes.', 'JH', '2', 'ゾウ', 'にく.む、にく.い、にく.らしい、にく.しみ', NULL, NULL),
('674', 'accustomed', '慣', '<img src=\"E685A3.png\" />', 'accustomed, Freud, state of mind, pierce, mother, breasts, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '14', '22', 'It took him awhile, but Data finally got ACCUSTOMED to his nipple/breast piercings. They were constantly rubbing up against his shirt and his heart-shaped locket. Picture Data, shirtless, squeezing his nipples in front of Picard and saying \"Yes, at first they were a bit shelly, but I´ve grown quite ACCUSTOMED to them\". That last bit should do it for you.', '5', '3', 'カン', 'な.れる、な.らす', NULL, NULL),
('675', 'pleasure', '愉', '<img src=\"E68489.png\" />', 'pleasure, Freud, state of mind, meeting, umbrella, butchers, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, sword, sabre, saber', '12', '22', 'At the meeting of butchers, in their narrow state of mind, they throw lame jokes around like, ´Oh hello, it´s a pleasure to meat you´, and find this rather pleasing.', 'JH', '1', 'ユ', 'たの.しい、たの.しむ', NULL, NULL),
('676', 'lazy', '惰', '<img src=\"E683B0.png\" />', 'lazy, Freud, state of mind, left-handed, left, by one’s side, craft, moon, month, flesh, part of the body', '12', '22', 'When I am in a LAZY state of mind I use my left hand to play with my meat...it feels like someone else is doing it, which is good cause I´m to lazy to get a date.', 'JH', '1', 'ダ', '', NULL, NULL),
('677', 'humility', '慎', '<img src=\"E6858E.png\" />', 'humility, Freud, state of mind, true, truth, ten, needle, eye, tool, animal legs, eight', '13', '22', 'Humility is the state of mind of accepting the truth about yourself - both favorable and unfavorable. (tweaked version of Raichu´s).', 'JH', '1', 'シン', 'つつし.む、つつし、つつし.み', NULL, NULL),
('678', 'remorse', '憾', '<img src=\"E686BE.png\" />', 'remorse, Freud, state of mind, emotion, march, mouth, heart', '16', '22', 'Remorse is the state of mind where I feel bad for what I did while I was tired and emotional!', 'JH', '1', 'カン', 'うら.む', NULL, NULL),
('679', 'recollection', '憶', '<img src=\"E686B6.png\" />', 'recollection, Freud, state of mind, idea, sound, vase, stand up, sun, day, heart', '16', '22', 'Recollection is about bringing ideas back to your mind.', 'JH', '1', 'オク', '', NULL, NULL),
('68', 'ten thousand', '万', '<img src=\"E4B887.png\" />', 'ten thousand, one, ceiling, bound up', '3', '4', 'I bound ten thousand dollars together and hid it under the floor.', '2', '5', 'マン、バン', 'よろず', NULL, NULL),
('680', 'disquieting', '惧', '<img src=\"E683A7.png\" />', '', '11', '22', 'My mind found the tool disquieting.', 'JH', '', 'ク', 'おそ.れる', NULL, NULL),
('681', 'yearn', '憧', '<img src=\"E686A7.png\" />', 'yearn, Freud, state of mind, juvenile, vase, stand up, computer', '15', '22', 'A paedophile´s state of mind is to yearn for juveniles.', 'JH', '1', 'ショウ、トウ、ドウ', 'あこが.れる', NULL, NULL),
('682', 'hanker', '憬', '<img src=\"E686AC.png\" />', '', '15', '22', 'My mind hankers for sunrise over the capital.', 'JH', '', 'ケイ', 'あこが.れる', NULL, NULL),
('683', 'pining', '慕', '<img src=\"E68595.png\" />', 'pining, graveyard, flowers, sun, day, large, St. Bernard, valentine', '14', '22', 'Pining, yearn for... etc. Presumably for lost love. An easy one here, someone standing in the graveyard, placing an old valentine card amonst all the existing tributes.', 'JH', '1', 'ボ', 'した.う', NULL, NULL),
('684', 'annexed', '添', '<img src=\"E6B7BB.png\" />', 'annexed, water, water droplets, water pistol, heavens, valentine', '11', '22', 'Hawaii is a little drop of heaven nestled in the waters of the Pacific, most often visited by honeymooners and valentines. It was annexed to the U.S.A. in 1959, and more recently to Japan as well-- albeit only unofficially, and through private commercial holdings.', 'JH', '1', 'テン', 'そ.える、そ.う、も.える、も.う', NULL, NULL),
('685', 'invariably', '必', '<img src=\"E5BF85.png\" />', 'invariably, heart, stick, drop, fishhook, drop3', '5', '22', 'You swear you´ll be in love forever, but invariably there comes a time when your heart is divided.', '4', '3', 'ヒツ', 'かなら.ず', NULL, NULL),
('686', 'ooze', '泌', '<img src=\"E6B38C.png\" />', 'ooze, water, water droplets, water pistol, invariably, heart, stick, drop, fishhook, drop3', '8', '22', 'Anything full of water will invariably begin to ooze.', 'JH', '1', 'ヒツ、ヒ', '', NULL, NULL),
('687', 'hand', '手', '<img src=\"E6898B.png\" />', 'hand', '4', '23', 'This pictograph actually really works if you look at it as a hand with fingers spread and middle finger pointing down. see the very top stroke as the edge of a shirt cuff, and it will all come together.', '1', '4', 'シュ、ズ', 'て、て-、-て、た-', NULL, NULL),
('688', 'watch over', '看', '<img src=\"E79C8B.png\" />', 'watch over, hand, eye', '9', '23', 'It´s a hot day of summer with a clear sky, you´re sitting outside a cafe (or maybe on a reclining chair in the garden), and you watch over the kids with a hand covering your eyes from the sunlight (next time, don´t forget the sunglasses).', '6', '1', 'カン', 'み.る', NULL, NULL),
('689', 'chafe', '摩', '<img src=\"E691A9.png\" />', 'chafe, hemp, cave, grove, tree, wood, hand, tree2, wood2', '15', '23', 'If you grind the hemp without a stone but use your hand instead it will chafe. (Image: \"Robin, why are your hands all chafed?\" ´Uh... (I´ve been grinding hemp all day)´).', 'JH', '1', 'マ', 'ま.する、さ.する、す.る', NULL, NULL),
('69', 'phrase', '句', '<img src=\"E58FA5.png\" />', 'phrase, bound up, mouth', '5', '4', 'Some Japanese phrases are difficult to wrap your mouth around.', '5', '1', 'ク', '', NULL, NULL),
('690', 'ego', '我', '<img src=\"E68891.png\" />', 'ego, hand, fiesta', '7', '23', 'Someone with a huge EGO is too good for any romantic partner and as such has nothing but personal \"hand fiestas\" with himself every night.', '6', '1', 'ガ', 'われ、わ、わ.が-、わが-', NULL, NULL),
('691', 'righteousness', '義', '<img src=\"E7BEA9.png\" />', 'righteousness, sheep, ego, hand, fiesta', '13', '23', 'Righteous Christians are sheep with egos (reworked from raulir, fixes word order to match radical order).', '5', '1', 'ギ', '', NULL, NULL),
('692', 'deliberation', '議', '<img src=\"E8ADB0.png\" />', 'deliberation, say, words, keitai, mouth, righteousness, sheep, ego, hand, fiesta', '20', '23', 'Careful deliberation produces words of righteousness.', '4', '3', 'ギ', '', NULL, NULL),
('693', 'sacrifice', '犠', '<img src=\"E78AA0.png\" />', 'sacrifice, cow, righteousness, sheep, ego, hand, fiesta', '17', '23', 'A cow that is righteous sacrifices her milk for the human race.', 'JH', '1', 'ギ、キ', 'いけにえ', NULL, NULL),
('694', 'rub', '抹', '<img src=\"E68AB9.png\" />', 'rub, finger, fingers, extremity, one, tree, wood', '8', '23', 'I like to RUB my FINGERS over my EXTREMITIES ....like my extremity-ly long, umm, hair.... This has been edited in response to being reported ...you can change \"hair\" to whatever extremity-ly long body part you like.', 'JH', '1', 'マツ', '', NULL, NULL),
('695', 'wipe', '拭', '<img src=\"E68BAD.png\" />', 'wipe, finger, fingers, style, arrow, craft', '9', '23', 'Why carry a handkerchief? I wipe my nose finger-style.', 'JH', '', 'ショク、シキ', 'ぬぐ.う、ふ.く', NULL, NULL),
('696', 'yank', '拉', '<img src=\"E68B89.png\" />', '', '8', '23', 'He quickly yanked his fingers out of the vase. Maybe no one noticed the attempt to steal the cookies...', 'JH', '', 'ラ、 ラツ、 ロウ', 'くだ.く、 ひし.ぐ、 らっ.する', NULL, NULL),
('697', 'embrace', '抱', '<img src=\"E68AB1.png\" />', 'embrace, finger, fingers, wrap, bound up, snake, self', '8', '23', 'When embracing someone, wrap your fingers around her butt for added effect. You may think of \"bound with snakes\" as a description of the fingers slithering around the buttocks, if you want a particularly graphic image.', 'JH', '3', 'ホウ', 'だ.く、いだ.く、かか.える', NULL, NULL),
('698', 'board', '搭', '<img src=\"E690AD.png\" />', 'board, finger, fingers, flowers, fit, meeting, umbrella, one, mouth', '12', '23', 'Ok, this is a little wierd, but i took this back to the kanji for pagoda (#254). I think it helps simplify the image, and also helps anchor the pagoda kanji in memory better as an added bonus. say this aloud once, and i think it will bring out a vivid image very quickly: \"Now boarding the pagoda ride. Please keep your fingers inside at all times...\".', 'JH', '1', 'トウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('699', 'extract', '抄', '<img src=\"E68A84.png\" />', 'extract, finger, fingers, few', '7', '23', 'You can extract her juices by inserting a few fingers.', 'JH', '1', 'ショウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('7', 'seven', '七', '<img src=\"E4B883.png\" />', 'seven, diced', '2', '1', 'This kanji is our good old seven, turned upside down.', '1', '5', 'シチ', 'なな、なな.つ、なの', NULL, NULL),
('70', 'texture', '肌', '<img src=\"E8828C.png\" />', 'texture, moon, month, flesh, part of the body, wind', '6', '4', 'When you expose your flesh to the wind it gets textured: goosebumps!', 'JH', '2', 'キ', 'はだ', NULL, NULL),
('700', 'confront', '抗', '<img src=\"E68A97.png\" />', 'confront, finger, fingers, whirlwind, top hat, wind', '7', '23', 'Gandalf confronts the evil beast, shouting \"you shall not pass!\". He holds up a single finger and sends forth a whirlwind.', 'JH', '1', 'コウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('701', 'criticism', '批', '<img src=\"E689B9.png\" />', 'criticism, finger, fingers, compare, spoon, sitting on the ground, spoon2, sitting on the ground2', '7', '23', 'Think of the two most famous critics, Ebert and Roeper. On their show, they compare thumbs (which are technically fingers) with each other before dispensing criticism.', '6', '1', 'ヒ', '', NULL, NULL),
('702', 'beckon', '招', '<img src=\"E68B9B.png\" />', 'beckon, finger, fingers, summon, seduce, sword, dagger, mouth', '8', '23', 'A Geisha beckons you with her index finger, and as you approach she runs her fingers all over her body in an attempt to seduce you. Keyword meaning : “invite”.', '5', '3', 'ショウ', 'まね.く', NULL, NULL),
('703', 'clear the land', '拓', '<img src=\"E68B93.png\" />', 'clear the land, finger, fingers, stone, rock', '8', '23', 'A huge index finger coming down from the sky is kicking boulders of rock, clearing the land. Maybe it´s the finger of God preparing a place for his little people to live.', 'JH', '1', 'タク', 'ひら.く', NULL, NULL),
('704', 'clap', '拍', '<img src=\"E68B8D.png\" />', 'clap, finger, fingers, white, dove', '8', '23', '(Image: the most snooty prim and proper English Lord with white gloves clapping only with his fingers. \"Oh bravo old chap. Bravo...\").', 'JH', '1', 'ハク、ヒョウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('705', 'strike', '打', '<img src=\"E68993.png\" />', 'strike, finger, fingers, street, nail, spike', '5', '23', 'You´re using a hammer to drive a nail into a plank, but you miss and strike your fingers, ouch ! PS: the character does not mean \"to go on strike\", it will be very helpful in the long run to create images that convey the proper sense of the character!', '3', '3', 'ダ、ダアス', 'う.つ、う.ち-、ぶ.つ', NULL, NULL),
