('772', 'stalk', '茎', '<img src=\"E88C8E.png\" />', 'stalk, flowers, spool, clod, toilet paper, crotch, soil, dirt, ground', '8', '23', 'Suggestion: Replace \"spool\" with \"toilet paper/roll\". Reasons: (1) Toilet paper/roll usually comes on a spool. (2) Toilet paper is used to clean the soil off your crotch. Story: Just get a flower and carefully wrap some toilet paper around its stalk. Spool also appears in suspicious (#716), lightly (#717), diameter (#882), sutra (#1360).', 'JH', '1', 'ケイ、キョウ', 'くき', NULL, NULL),
('773', 'suspicious', '怪', '<img src=\"E680AA.png\" />', 'suspicious, Freud, state of mind, spool, clod, toilet paper, crotch, soil, dirt, ground', '8', '23', 'When you´re suspicious, your state of mind twists round and round like a spool of thread.', 'JH', '1', 'カイ、ケ', 'あや.しい、あや.しむ', NULL, NULL),
('774', 'lightly', '軽', '<img src=\"E8BBBD.png\" />', 'lightly, car, spool, clod, toilet paper, crotch, soil, dirt, ground', '12', '23', 'Fact: this kanji is used to denote a certain class of vehicles in Japan whose engines are under a certain size (less than 750cc I think) and are called light vehicles here. Imagine a so-called light vehicle or a light-truck with a load of spools driving down a road ever so lightly, careful not to let any of the spools roll out onto the street.', '3', '2', 'ケイ', 'かる.い、かろ.やか、かろ.んじる', NULL, NULL),
('775', 'uncle', '叔', '<img src=\"E58F94.png\" />', 'uncle, above, small, little, crotch', '8', '23', 'Oh come on people - say what we´ve all been thinking: the uncle is that creepy guy towering above a little one´s crotch.', 'JH', '1', 'シュク', '', NULL, NULL),
