('779', 'anti-', '反', '<img src=\"E58F8D.png\" />', 'anti-, demonstation, cliff, crotch', '4', '23', 'I think of an anti-hero (Dirty Harry etc.) for this primitive, whose trademark for disposing of villians is not an honorable fight, but a kick in the crotch and then a shove off a cliff (perhaps whilst the villain´s back is turned).', '3', '3', 'ハン、ホン、タン、ホ', 'そ.る、そ.らす、かえ.す、かえ.る、-かえ.る', NULL, NULL),
