('809', 'commence', '始', '<img src=\"E5A78B.png\" />', 'commence, woman, pedestal, elbow, mouth', '8', '23', 'Many men, before they commence their relationship with the woman of their desires, place her on something of a pedestal, which often leads to disappointment later on.', '3', '4', 'シ', 'はじ.める、-はじ.める、はじ.まる', NULL, NULL),
