('811', 'window', '窓', '<img src=\"E7AA93.png\" />', 'window, hole, house, human legs, elbow, heart', '11', '23', 'The top primitive is similar to hole (#1316). A window is a hole (#1316) in your house that you occassionally sit next to while leaning on your ELBOW and gazing out, a picture of a lonely HEARTedness.', '6', '3', 'ソウ、ス', 'まど、てんまど、けむだし', NULL, NULL),
