('845', 'poverty', '貧', '<img src=\"E8B2A7.png\" />', 'poverty, part, eight, sword, dagger, shellfish, clam, oyster, eye, animal legs, eight', '11', '24', 'In the case of true poverty, not having money is only part of the problem. There are other components as well, like lack of education, class structuring, etc., but that doesn´t really matter. Just remember that the money is only part of it, not the whole.', '5', '3', 'ヒン、ビン', 'まず.しい', NULL, NULL),
