('849', 'venerable old man', '翁', '<img src=\"E7BF81.png\" />', 'venerable old man, public, eight, elbows, feathers, wings', '10', '24', 'The venerable old man is the public figure head of the Native American Village, answering all questions and solving all problems. The higher in rank you get in this tribe, the more feathers decorate you. Imagine this old man covered in beautiful feathers.', 'JH', '1', 'オウ', 'おきな', NULL, NULL),
