('855', 'longing', '欲', '<img src=\"E6ACB2.png\" />', 'longing, valley, eight, umbrella, mouth, lack, yawn', '11', '24', 'Guess what? Japanese has dirty words too! (In fact, a lot of them) A sexual story is NOT inappropriate here, as this kanji is very sexual, such as in 性欲; lust. As for a story: the lack of contact with a woman´s valley will leave a man LONGING for love.', '6', '3', 'ヨク', 'ほっ.する、ほ.しい', NULL, NULL),
('856', 'abundant', '裕', '<img src=\"E8A395.png\" />', 'abundant, cloak, valley, eight, umbrella, mouth', '12', '24', 'Again using the fact that cleavage in Japanese is called \"valley of the chest\": a woman with abundant cleavage tightly wraps up her bosom in a form-fitting cloak, but leaving her valley exposed. Another unforgettable image (thank you, thank you, I´ll be here all week).', 'JH', '1', 'ユウ', '', NULL, NULL),
('857', 'lead (metal)', '鉛', '<img src=\"E9899B.png\" />', 'lead, metal, gold, gully, eight, mouth', '13', '24', 'Picture the molten lead (the heavy metal) being discreetly drained out of the factory into a gully behind.', 'JH', '1', 'エン', 'なまり', NULL, NULL),
